"{\"movie_id\": 0, \"paragraphs\": [{\"header\": \"NA\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Rev. 042987  Above The Law Screenplay by Steven Pressfield and Ronald Shusett and Andrew Davis Story by Andrew Davis and Steven Seagal Warner Bros. Inc. 4000 Warner Boulevard Burbank, California 91522 Final Draft March 27, 1987 Warner Bros. Inc. All Rights Reserved Above The Law Fade In: Titles Sequence - Montage With Score Photographic Stills show us Nicola Toscani as a city boy in various growing-up Shots, circa 1950's -- with street chums wearing a Wyatt Earp T-shirt, in a communion suit. Then: in his first qi, a youngster studying the martial arts; he grows, we see news clippings of him winning trophies, his name on contest posters, Shots of him in action. Then: Japan. being dumped on his butt, posing smiling beside Japanese martial artists, then himself as an instructor. Now: a few military uniforms enter the picture, we see security clearance documents with Nico's picture and name on them. Then Nico near draft age with an American friend Nelson Fox on some kind of training base. Titles End. Nico now in his teens, studying with real masters, Dissolve To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. JUNGLE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Blowing through the roof of a dense jungle straight At Camera, Helicopter Rotors Rise to a Deafening Pitch. Super: whips in the fierce downdraft as -- Viet - Cambodian Border, 1972. Jungle foliage \\\"Huey\\\" Gunship with Us Army markings becomes discernible. The chopper lowers toward a crude landing zone hacked out of the wilderness. We Glimpse Cambodian troops and several machine gun positions around the Lz.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. JUNGLE - TWO ARMED AMERICANS - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"watch from the edge of the landing zone. We recognize Nico and Fox, now in their twenties, dressed in the nonmilitary jungle attire that usually marks a Cia \\\"spook.\\\" Helicopter touches down. their mid-thirties, all carrying some kind of medical bags -- disembark into the Howling Rotor Blast. They hit the ground nimbly, as if they've done it many times before. Three Older Americans -- rough-looking, in Leader Of Three wears a khaki cowboy hat and packs a pearl-handled .45. Nico And Fox don't know whether to react with laughter or uneasiness\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You ever see chemical interrogation before?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico's eyes stay on the approaching \\\"cowboy,\\\" Kurt Zagon, for whom he plainly feels an instant animosity. These assholes are agency\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico'S Pov\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Follows the medical bag in the cowboy's hand. Back To Fox And Nico Fox We're all C.I.A. But these guys are from a page that ain't on the map.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. JUNGLE - LATE AFTERNOON\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico in the point, leading Fox and the three Cit (Chemical Interrogation Team) men down an unmarked, twisting trail. We see from Nico's gait that he is athletic, a born leader and totally at home in the jungle. Trail - Late Afternoon snakes along a ridge line, high enough to give us a view and let us know these guys are way out in the boonies. How long till we're across the border\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"We've been over for the past hour\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"The group continues along the ridge.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Cut To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. JUNGLE - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The sky glows from nearby bomb attacks. Nico listening hard -- and even sniffing the air -- glances back at Zagon, who stands impatiently, drawing on a cigarette. What are you looking at, hotshot\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Why don't you light a bonfire?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(indicates cigarette glow) Irritably, Zagon ditches his smoke. Just drive the taxi, ace\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"As the party moves out, Fox flashes Nico a look as if to say, \\\"Don't fuck with these guys.\\\"\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. CAMBODIAN BASE CAMP - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A pocket-fortified position. Armed Cambodian lookouts, several hooches, radio equipment. Nico leads the party in through the perimeter. Zagon eyes the layout like he's seen 100 of them. Fox indicates a hooch\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"They're in there.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The three Cit men start for the hooch. Nico casts a concerned glance around at the base camp troops, looking sloppy as hell. I don't trust these yo-yo's\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Full Shot - Base Camp\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"We see Nico moving like a shadow from one defensive position to another, checking the perimeter. We can vaguely hear him Rousting the Cambodian lookouts, speaking in dialect. Defensive Position - Nico hears a Sound, looks back toward the hooch. Nico'S Pov - Hooch Two Asian prisoners, stripped to the waist, babbling in- coherently, are dragged out the back by a pair of Cambodian guards and hustled off into the darkness. Voices can be heard inside the hooch. A single lantern glowing inside gives the hut a creepy, frightening aspect. Back To Nico He's extremely uneasy about what's about to happen inside the hooch.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. HOOCH - CLOSE ON RICKETY CARD TABLE - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"on which are spread a terrifying array of syringes, drug vials and surgical instruments. Zagon's hand picks up a hypodermic, squirt-tests it. Two Asian Prisoners are on their knees, shirtless, handcuffed with heavy nylon tape to a stake driven into the ground in the center of the hooch. first prisoner by the shoulders. Zagon injects the first prisoner. Zagon watches with professional satisfaction. One of the subordinate Cit men moves in, grabs the Instantly the man begins shivering, convulsing\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"That's the nice thing about modern technology. You don't have to wait for results.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He moves close to the first prisoner\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Where is it, Charley? You got six tons of our shit --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The prisoner tries to speak, but he's in such torment all that comes out is a blood-curdling wail --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. BAST CAMP - NICO\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"hears this horrifying cry. He starts swiftly toward the hooch --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. HOOCH - INTERPRETER\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"has moved as close to Zagon and the first prisoner as a fight referee to two boxers. The prisoner is convulsing wildly. Zagon grabs him fiercely by the hair. Don't you die on me, fucker -\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"What the hell's wrong\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"This pussy can't hold his liquor.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(throws the prisoner down) The first prisoner is plainly in a death spasm. Nico enters at this point. He takes in the scene quickly, moves to a spot beside the entrance. Zagon doesn't look at Nico, but it's plain he is aware of Nico's presence. It is as if he wants to prove something to this muscular kid -- and prove it to the others, too. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 First Prisoner dies in agony on the ground. Second Prisoner watches with eyes like flint. He is in his mid-forties, scarred, missing several fingers. Probably a colonel or higher, he looks like he's been fighting these round-eyes since the French in the 50's. He is plainly one tough The second prisoner meets Zagon's eyes, as if customer. daring him to use the drugs on him, too. Zagon eyes the prisoner with barely contained hatred. The prisoner doesn't back down an inch\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"So my little doctor bag doesn't scare you, eh? Well I don't need it to open your yap.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Zagon reaches to a scabbard on his Western belt, pulls out a fearsome serrated blade -- a cross between a bowie knife and a scalpel. blade in the lantern light. He steps toward the prisoner, displaying the Nico watches impassively\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Where's our load, you sack of slime? What did you do with my shit? --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Zagon punches the prisoner full in the face, holding the knife handle in his fist to double the force of the blow and to terrify him with the proximity of the blade. The prisoner crashes sideways, face bloody -\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I'm gonna teach you good. I'm gonna teach you never to fuck with my opium --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Fox And Two Cit Men seem to know exactly what this is about. Nico didn't know, but the new kid on the block is catching on fast. Nico has difficulty containing his emotion. Zagon stands over the prisoner, as if daring him to get back up. The prisoner gets back to his knees, bloody eyes meeting Zagon's with defiance -\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You're a hard nigger, aren't you, boy? You took it from the Chinks. you took it from the French. You'll be fucked if some Yankee peckerwood's gonna start your gums flapping --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico watches Zagon move the knife blade closer to the prisoner. Zagon -- Well, you're gonna chirp for me, tough guy. You're gonna sing like a choir -- Nico takes a step toward Zagon\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"What the fuck does this have to do with military intelligence\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Your orders are 'assist and observe' cherry --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Zagon turns to face Nico -\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Back off, partner --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Zagon turns from Nico. He moves close to the second prisoner, close as a lover, displaying the blade in the lamplight\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I'm gonna start carving at your ankles. We'll throw your feet in that box right over there. Then I'm gonna take off your arms --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"One of the Cit men yanks the prisoner's leg forward, clamping it to the ground with his hands. The prisoner still hasn't flinched. Zagon. He seems as locked into this dance of death as Nico (can't take much more) Fox -- Shut up, Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You can disappear as easy as this slope, kid --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Zagon starts for the prisoner. Here comes the blade. Suddenly -- Nico grabs Zagon's shoulder. Zagon spins with terrifying quickness, cocking the blade to slash at Nico. Before Zagon's blow even starts, Nico slams him with a ferocious elbow shot right under the jaw. Zagon literally comes off the ground, Nico's blow is so terrific. Zagon drops in an unconscious heap. In a flash the two other Cit men move to jump Nico. Smash! The second Cit man is swallowing his teeth. out of the hooch -- Fox leaps in the way of the third, shoves Nico\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. HOOCH - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Fox wrestles Nico away from the hooch -- Are you crazy?!\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"What the fuck's the matter with you?!!!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico is shaking with rage and fear. He takes several steps away from the hooch, then draws up abruptly. Nico pulls his .45 from his holster, pops the safety, starts back for the hooch -- Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I don't cap him now, he's gonna do me later.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The last Cit man appears, gun drawn, in the hooch doorway. Fox grabs Nico, hauls him back again -\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I'll cover this. Get back to the L.Z. --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"-- I'll fix it! Get out! Get the fuck outa here! The Cit man calls out to the Cambodian troops, in dialect, pointing at Nico. The soldiers start toward Nico, as if to seize him. apparently countermanding the orders of the Cit men. The troops, confused, hold up for a moment. Fox, too, starts yelling to the troops in dialect\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I'll call for a chopper. get outa here!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Nico gives a last look, turns and takes off down the jungle trail. Nico disappears into the darkness. Fox seems abandoned. The Distant Bombing Continues\"}, {\"character\": \"FADE TO BLACK.\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Fade In On:\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Church Steeple - Day Tilt Down to reveal St. Elizabeth's, a huge parish church in an ItalianLatino neighborhood in Chicago. The church looks festive, we see a few formally-dressed people hurrying in, then a squad car pulls up. The cops run upstairs as if they're late --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. ST. MARY'S - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A baptism in progress. Nico -- 15 years older than when we last saw him, is standing beside Sara, his lovely wife -- watching a 60-ish priest, Father Genarro, finish the final ritual on Nico's infant son Julian. The priest straightens the baby's baptismal garment, tugging the cloth around the little fellow's crotch. Smiles from friends and relatives clustered proudly around. Several cops, some in uniform are amongst them. Nico grabs his son from Genarro with a theatrical protective motion, tugs up the little boy's garment, kisses him smack on the bare butt. Laughter from all as Nico holds the lad high and proud. He puts his arm around Sara.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. NICO'S HOUSE - BACK YARD - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Huge trays of Italian delicacies are carried out into the sunlight by several \\\"old country\\\"-type women. Wine is poured from generous carafes. Friends and relatives are everywhere, laughing and enjoying themselves; apparently the party has come here straight from the church. Presents for the new baby are being opened by Nico's wife, Sara, and Nico's mother, Rosa. Mama, look at this -- all done by hand\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Sara lifts a cute baby outfit\"}, {\"character\": \"ROSA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Nico had one just like this. Thank you, Cora.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Cora, an aunt, proudly smiles\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Holding the baby. Realizes that his little son has pooped in his pants.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He turns for help to Sara. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 I think we got a little problem here\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"I carried him for the last nine months, you take him for the next diaper.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Assorted uncles and aunts watch with amusement as Nico tries awkwardly to deal with the problem\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"That's what you get for not marrying a Sicilian.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sara lets Nico struggle a moment, then takes over\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"My brave husband. He's not afraid of thieves and muggers, but he's terrified when his son poops in his pants.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Toscani relatives look on with approval at the happy couple and their baby. Another Part Of Back Yard Three Chicago cops, Lukich and Henderson in plain clothes and Lieutenant Strozah in uniform wolf some Italian goodies while eying the group of celebrating relatives. Lukich (indicates Nico across the patio) Toscani holds the record. for havin' more relatives under federal indictment than any other cop in Chicago. Two Of Nico'S Uncles Branca and Luigi, who look like they have been on the other side of a cop's work, are in turn eying Lukich and Henderson -- plus a cluster of other cops in civvies hovering around the buffet table like vultures\"}, {\"character\": \"BRANCA\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Look at these stiff dicks. A free meal and they come out like flies.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Street Outside Nico'S House - Day An unmarked police car pulls up. Dolores Jackson , another undercover cop, tall, black, and elegant, enters the driveway leading to Nico's back yard -- Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Back Yard Jackson enters. intelligence. Strozah, and a couple of other cops. She's impeccably dressed and radiates She's greeted warmly by Lukich, Henderson\"}, {\"character\": \"STROZAH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I didn't do nothing, Counselor. I'm clean\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Eight more days, Lieutenant. You better start preparing your defense.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Baby, I'm gonna put you on retainer\"}, {\"character\": \"HENDERSON\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You passed the bar? I make it a point never to pass the bar.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson sees Nico and Sara across the yard, waves and starts toward them -- Back To Branca And Luigi Luigi indicates Jackson as she crosses the patio\"}, {\"character\": \"LUIGI\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Now this cop. She can bust me any day.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nick, Sara And Rosa  Jackson comes up, makes a theatrical appreciation of Nico's stylish attire, kisses Sara and greets Nico's mom warmly. She starts oohing and ahhing over the baby\"}, {\"character\": \"VARIOUS SHOTS\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Young kids playing on the lawn, more guests arriving, Father Genarro dancing with an elderly matron. We see that Nico's friends are an electric mix. Cops, art-y types, people of varied ages and professions.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Back To Jackson Holding the baby\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Look at this little bundle. What a cupcake\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You give up being the D.A. and hurry up and find the right fella, Jax. You might have time for one of these yourself.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987 10A\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Nico, will you let the woman catch her breath?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Japanese Woman  moves in shyly on the fringe of the cluster. While Jackson and Sara continue their \\\"mom\\\" talk, Nico edges off toward Watanabe, shaking her hand with real pleasure. Watanabe! Say hey, Doc\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"They begin jabbering in Japanese.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"We will meet Watanabe again later. She's a brainy-looking woman -- reserved, a bit mysterious -- who talks quietly and intensely in Japanese with Nico like they're old friends who go back a long way. Above The Law - Rev. 41787\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. TOSCANI FRONT PORCH - LATER\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Branca, Luigi and several other Toscani patriarchs smoke cigars and sip beer in a cluster. Nico holds Julian\"}, {\"character\": \"BRANCA\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You're a father now. Are you gonna take me up on my offer?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I'm happy, Branca. I like what I do\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Branca glances seriously to the other uncles, then, with a smile, pats Nico's cheek\"}, {\"character\": \"BRANCA\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Look at this face! Six-foot-four, pretty as the statue of David. And he's a cop!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Branca laughs. nothing. observe and try to listen. From a distance, Watanabe watches, missing Across the porch, Lukich and several other cops Branca This face should be sticking up from a white shirt. It should be a banker, a businessman, someone who earns a decent living for his family! We're happy\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"LUIGI\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nickels and dimes. Your wife's a woman with class. What did she run -- a ballet school.?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"An art gallery\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"BRANCA\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Same thing. She wants a husband who carries a briefcase, not a shoulder holster.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson watches Nico trying to keep his good humor. This is serious stuff, despite the light tone. Branca's eyes meet Nico's. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Branca You wanted to get shot, you got shot. You wanted to get knifed, you got knifed. You've had your fun. Basta! Enough! Let your family help you, Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"UNCLE GUISEPPE\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Uncle Gio, that kind of help I don't need. I don't know.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I'd rather get shot by someone Jackson and Lukich crack up. The others follow. For the moment, the tension is dispelled.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. NICO'S HOUSE - UPSTAIRS - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico comes out of the bedroom, adjusting his shoulder holster, tugging his jacket over it. He sees his mother standing near the head of the stairs, just outside another bedroom door. Concern on her face\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"What are you doing in here, Mama? Go join the party.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico comes down the hall, tucking in his shirt -- stops to give his mother a squeeze. O.S. from the bedroom: the sound of Quiet Sobbing. Nico glances in.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. NURSERY - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sara and another woman sit on the bed, comforting a 60-ish grandmother Zingaro, who is crying. Nico comes in. He kneels before Mrs. Zingaro, concerned. Mrs. Z\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Is this a way to act on the day of my son's baptism?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The poor woman can't meet Nico's eyes. It's Lucy. She's gone again\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Nico glances from Sara to Rosa.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Mrs. Zingaro shakes her head, choked with pain. Nico holds her, looking over her shoulder toward Sara\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"It's that kid from the bar on Damen? The one with the drugs?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Sara doesn't know. Nico does. He comforts Mrs. Zingaro another moment, then stands\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Listen to me, Mrs. Z. Are you listening?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(as the woman nods miserably) I have to go to work now. But I'll come by tonight. You'll be at the bakery? Si, Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"MRS. ZINGARO\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"We'll talk, okay? We'll find a way to take care of this.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico kisses Mrs. Z. He takes Sara's hand in goodbye, starts for the door.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. NICO'S HOUSE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Festivities still in progress. Nico passes through, nodding, thanking people for coming, taking farewells. Jackson waits for him, glancing at her watch.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. UNMARKED CAR - MOVING\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico is driving. Jackson checks in on the radio\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Unit Ten Tango X-ray. We're up and clear.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. VARIOUS STREETS - UNMARKED CAR\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"moves into the central city. Pov Through Car Windows - Streets - Moving Bad-looking hombres on stoops, street corners\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I promised the Lieutenant, I'm gonna take care of you. Broken windows and lost kittens for your last week.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Widen Shot to include Nico and Jackson\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"And then you're gonna come visit me in a nice, clean, air conditioned office --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. STREET - BUCKSHOT'S LIQUORS - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The unmarked car pulls up outside a liquor store and bar.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. UNMARKED CAR\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"as it parks. stopping at this dive for\\\"? Jackson gives Nico a look: \\\"What are we Nico I gotta take a quick leak. Stay put. He gets out of the car, starts for the bar.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. BUCKSHOT'S LIQUORS - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Dim, smoke-choked, dangerous characters at the bar. Nico enters. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 His silk shirt and sport coat clash with the druggy, working- class attire of the bar's denizens. Hard faces check him out subtly, ignore him. Nico approaches the bartender, shows a photograph. The bartender shakes his head\"}, {\"character\": \"BAD DUDE\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Why the fuck don't you assholes leave me alone?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He continues mouthing off to Nico. Nico moves to one stool, then another; the same exchange is repeated. Favor One Particularly Tough Customer A hulking bruiser with an earring. He watches as