o. hand. ping each one violently, spitting, raging for them to attack. But no one attacks. Nico has Lucy's photo in his He jams it in one man's face, then another's, slap\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You seen the top of her head, huh? Like I seen your mother's --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Or was it yours? Or yours? (slaps him fero- ciously) I couldn't tell, it looked like her ass -- Nico rages like a beast\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Come on, motherfuckers. Do it. Do it!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"One man -- Nico lunges for the Bad Dude, grabs him like he's about to tear his face off -\"}, {\"character\": \"BAD DUDE\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Upstairs!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"She's upstairs! 4-D! Nico drags the Dude from behind the bar. Holding him, Nico turns, glowering, to all\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You cocksuckers are brave enough with 14-year-old girls.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"55A\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. FLOPHOUSE HALLWAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico throws Bad Dude down the hallway in front of him.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. FOURTH-FLOOR APARTMENT - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The door bursts in from a jackhammer kick. Nico stands in the hallway. shaking. Bad Dude stands next to him; hurt\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Get outta here.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"We look in the apartment. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 16A. Reverse - Nico'S Pov A young Pimp -- quite handsome in a boyish way -- stares up in panic from a grimy mattress on the floor. Little Lucy is in bra and panties, strung out, 14 and beautiful. Syringes and free-base paraphernalia are on a table. Nico In Doorway 