acter\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico hears something through the earphones. Gestures for silence -- Angle Through Office Window Chi Chi listens with increased intensity to something on the phone. He starts writing it down -- Back To Nico In unmarked car. He's writing it down too. I got the shipment\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"What\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"What's he saying\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"'. Engine block has cleared customs. Serial number Va-748. Pick up Tuesday, 3 May as authorized.'\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. BODY SHOP - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Chi Chi emerges from the office, tucking a scrap of paper into his pocket. Abandano follows. They get into a late-model Lincoln which pulls out onto the street.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. STREET - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Jackson's car follows at a discreet distance. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Nico  Unit Ten Tango X-ray. I need a vehicle registration I.D. Go ahead, please\"}, {\"character\": \"POLICE RADIO\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"'86 Lincoln. Illinois 354 Dog '67.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico \"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. UNMARKED CAR - MOVING - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson picks up Nico's pad to take down the response. After a moment\"}, {\"character\": \"POLICE RADIO\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Vehicle registration follows. Leaseholder: Ramon Testamente, registered alien. Nation of origin: Venezuela. Do you wish criminal record search\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I want to know when he wipes his behind.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Series Of Shots As Nico and Jackson tail the Lincoln out of the industrial zone into a fancier, non-Latin neighborhood. On the sidewalks we glimpse theatergoers, fashionable white couples out on the town\"}, {\"character\": \"LINCOLN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Pulls up to a valet park outside a ton-y restaurant. A sign says:\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"\\\"Bogota.\\\"\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. UNMARKED CAR - MOVING\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Jackson exchange a glance. Salvano? Jackpot\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"NA\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. RESTAURANT - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Chi Chi and Abandano get out of their car, a valet takes it, Chi Chi enters the restaurant.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. SALVANO'S RESTAURANT - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Jackson enter the main dining room, which we recognize from the scene with Nardo the busboy. The place is packed with fashionable people of all races. A band plays salsa; couples dance. Nico and Jackson pass easily as a hip \\\"uptown\\\" couple. A pretty Latin Hostess approaches them. Two for dinner\"}, {\"character\": \"HOSTESS\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Two for drinks\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"They elbow up to the packed bar, standing. Nico squints toward the rear dining room.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico'S Pov - Down Bar Looking past numerous patrons, we see Chi Chi whisper something to a waiter and take a seat at a rear table The waiter hurries off into a back hallway. Nico And Jackson - At Bar Jackson moves to the salsa beat. A Barmaid approaches. Gimme something stiff. I need it\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Who doesn't\"}, {\"character\": \"BARMAID\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico's eyes never leave Chi Chi.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Rear Dining Room From the back hallway Salvano emerges -- in his tux, looking prosperous. He sits down beside Chi Chi and Abandano. words, Chi Chi removes the scrap of paper from his pocket, hands it to Salvano. A waitress brings two drinks. After a few Nico  You'll have your engine block next Tuesday, boss. Back To Nico And Jackson As the Barmaid brings their drinks. Jackson sees her peaceful week to retirement flying out the window\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Why couldn't it be a week from Tuesday? I could read about it in the paper.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico grabs her waist, pulls her onto the dance floor, and does a playful twirl. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Nico Cheer up, partner. I'm gonna make you famous.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. WHOLESALE MEAT AREA - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Track spurs, greasy streets, parked fork lifts. 94A\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. ROOF - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Lieutenant Strozah surveys the street traffic. Nico, Jackson And Lukich The two men, dressed as meat processors in hard hats and bloody white coats, rake cattle guts under the eave of a packing plant. carrying a clipboard, inspects a few hanging carcasses. Jackson, dressed like a Usda Inspector and You missed a few spots, boys\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I'm takin' it home t'a make kilbasa, boss.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Luke casts an impatient glance across the street to a lot with four parked meat trucks. We glimpse two \\\"truckers\\\" keeping low in the shadows of one cab. Down the block a seemingly empty pickup truck is parked in an alley\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"This ain't a bust -- it's a convention.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Don't you like company, Luke\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"We got all the scouts here -- Drug Enforcement Agency, the Alcohol, Tobacco and Firearms --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Keep this channel clear, Toscani. Walkie-Talkie  We realize Nico, Jackson and Lukich are wired, with mikes out of sight under their coats. Nico glances to the pick- up, near to which three men can be spotted in the alley. Apparently one of them is the walkie-talkie voice\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"This is our channel, dickhead. And our collar.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Another Walkie-Talkie  That's enough, all of you! Keep this channel clear. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 28A. Angle On Meat Plant - Day Nothing happening. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Another Angle Dead as hell. Nico, Lukich And Jackson Bored, pissed off, tired. Suddenly: Battered Van With Two Men emerges from a corner, two blocks down. It starts slowly this way. 1St Walkie-Talkie  All right. Everyone get their heads outa their ass. The meat truck men duck down out of sight, the pickup men back into the shadows. Nico and Lukich keep raking cow guts. The van passes slowly, checking out the area\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"'. And so I quit the police department. got myself a steady job -- '\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The van accelerates slightly, turns a corner, vanishes. Silence\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"They spotted me. I'm too good- looking to be a meat slopper.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Will you hot dogs shut up? 1St Walkie-Talkie  The van returns. On a cross street. Heading behind the packing plant\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You're too ugly.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Now a second car appears. The Lincoln. Behind it is an ancient station wagon. Both vehicles take a different cross street, but both heading behind the packing plant\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Here we go, boys and girls --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You stay put. As soon as the two vehicles pass out of sight, Nico and Lukich ditch their rakes, dart into the packing plant. The meat truck men Start their Truck. The pickup men board their vehicle -- Jackson follows Nico and Luke -- but at a safe distance.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. PACKING PLANT - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Lukich sprint in a crouch past the blood runoffs, meat cutting tables -- Nico'S Pov - Running Through the windows at the rear of the plant, we see the station wagon and the van, pulling up swiftly beside one another, men getting out --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. PLANT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Lukich draw their guns, running full-tilt\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"It's going down now. Move!\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. REAR OF PACKING PLANT - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The station wagon men heave their rear door open, the van men start to open their side door. The Lincoln is stopped at a distance. Suddenly -- Nico And Lukich burst from the rear door of the packing plant, guns drawn. Police\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Quick Cuts - Van And Station Wagon Men\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"grab for their weapons -- Cops In Meat Truck And Pickup come highballing around both sides of the packing plant -- Van And Station Wagon Men Open Fire. who's a cop and who's a criminal. There is confusion and mayhem; it's not clear Nico And Lukich dive for cover, Returning Fire. The Dea men in one truck also Open Up. Machine Gun Fire rakes the Dea truck; it spins out of control; flips. One of the van men is hit between the eyes. Lukich Shoots the machine-gunner\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"The Lincoln!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico! Lincoln starts to Peel Out. We glimpse Chi Chi in the driver's seat, Salvano on the passenger side. Nico steps in front of the accelerating Lincoln, raises his .45.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. LINCOLN - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Salvano and Chi Chi dive below the dash and continue forward. Fires blindly -- trying to hit Nico. Salvano, in the passenger seat, raises his Gun;\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. LINCOLN - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico Unloads his .45 into the windshield and the firewall. The Lincoln keeps coming down the narrow alley. Nico brazenly steps up onto the hood and dives, grabbing onto the roof.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. LINCOLN - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Salvano can't believe it. He screams something in Spanish. He Fires again, this time through the roof.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. LINCOLN - ROOF - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Bullet holes appear. Nico narrowly misses being hit. Another Angle - Lincoln Nico reaches over the side of the car and Smashes the pas- senger Window with his fist. Closeup - Nico'S Hand Salvano's face is bashed. Nico's huge hand grabs Salvano's throat; he won't let go. Closeup - Nico He hangs on with one hand. Closeup - Salvano Nico's fingers now dig into Salvano's larynx; he may never talk again. Chi Chi. order to save his boss. Chi Chi makes the decision to stop the car in He's gagging. Salvano now points the gun at Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Nico leaps off the roof pulling Salvano past the broken glass, out of the window. Several Police Vehicles Screech into the lot. Officers pour out, guns drawn, surrounding the Lincoln and the other vehicles. Jackson joins them, weapon in hand. Nico drags Salvano by the neck across the lot to the van, slamming the drug dealer up against the van's side. Lukich, Jackson and Strozah are there, with the Dea cops, all covering the other men\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"How many kilos you got in there, Skivuzo?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Salvano couldn't answer if he wanted to. The other cops look at Nico with awe. Lukich whips the van door open, yanks a tarp off the cargo.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. VAN\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The engine block sits in a wooden shipping frame, wrapped with industrial plastic. Nico climbs into the van, rips the plastic sheeting off, grabs the wood slats of the shipping frame, tears them off. In the background, ambulances are arriving to care for the wounded cops and criminals. Closeup - Engine Block From the cylinder heads emerges a full load, not of drugs, but of plastique tubes labeled U.S. Army C-4 High Explosive. Lukich, Jackson And Other Cops react with surprise and shock. Nico rips open one of tubes and smells it. Close - Nico Confused; frustrated. What kinda fuckin' high is this\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Cut To:\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. FBI OFFICE - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Opening On Salvano, in a chair, looking bruised and swollen, and wearing an expression of fuming indignation. Salvano -- I'll tell you what this cop is. He's a fucking menace! Two Fbi Agents  face Salvano, Chi Chi and the lawyer Abandano (apparently representing Salvano and Chi Chi). Neeley is on the phone. Pictures of Reagan and Meese are prominent on the wall. You see what he did to me?\"}, {\"character\": \"SALVANO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT HALLORAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Your problem is being handled right now, Mr. Salv -\"}, {\"character\": \"SALVANO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Well, it shoulda been\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Yeah? handled twelve hours ago. I don't know who's running this outfit, but somebody better get his goddamn wires straight! Agent Neeley -- yes, sir. yes, sir, I understand -\"}, {\"character\": \"SALVANO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"That maniac should be wearing a number, not a badge.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Salvano knows what the call is about. He straightens the tie beneath his bruised neck, assuming the attitude of a respectable citizen who has been unjustly wronged. Agent Neeley -- count on it, sir. Right. You'll have our full cooperation. Neeley hangs up. Glances dubiously to Halloran. Then turns grimly to Salvano, Chi Chi and the lawyer Abandano. You're free to go\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. FEDERAL BUILDING - LOBBY - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The hoods and their lawyer smugly walk past a cleaning woman. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 33A.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. PRECINCT CAPTAIN'S OFFICE - MORNING\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Opening On Agent Neeley's face. Composed, clean-cut, but intense, wearing a light-colored business suit. Pan To Agent Halloran -- the same upright, clean-shaven bureau look. The two men are seated to one side of Lieutenant Fred Strozah. Nico, Jackson, Lukich And Dea And Atf Men sit and stand in various postures in front of the Lieutenant's desk. Lieutenant Strozah -- This is no reflection on the work you officers have done. I feel, and the whole department feels, extremely proud of your initiative and gallantry. That \\\"spare me the horseshit\\\" look on Nico's face. He's fuming. Strozah sees Nico's bitter expression. It's on the others' faces too\"}, {\"character\": \"LIEUTENANT STROZAH\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"As all of you are well aware, possession of these explosives is a federal offense and under jurisdiction of the F.B.I.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico's eyes meet Lieutenant Strozah's. There's respect between the two, but it's plainly under a helluva strain\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Sir. brothers in the Bureau --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"With all respect to our (biting sarcasm; turns to Neeley) -- That's no answer. It's no answer to why one of the biggest dealers in the city is out on the street now, free as a bird! Agent Neeley stiffens\"}, {\"character\": \"LIEUTENANT STROZAH\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Keep it in your pants, Nico. These men have a job to do, just like us.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico stifles his outrage. The other cops exchange glances -- upset and angry. Agent Neeley clears his throat\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Lieutenant, I think these officers are entitled to a fuller explanation.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Agent Neeley  They've risked their lives. I understand one man is in the hospital. He speaks to the officers\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"What I'm about to say doesn't leave this room. Is that clear?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Assent from everyone\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Mr. Salvano has been working for some time in cooperation with certain federal agencies.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Close - Nico'S Face Stunned and furious at this royal fuck-up\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I'm not at liberty to divulge the nature of Mr. Salvano's involvement -- I just learned of its existence myself a few hours ago.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"But one thing I can tell you -- Back To Agent Neeley Agent Neeley Mr. Salvano's role is crucial to an extremely sensitive ongoing investigation. Any further surveillance, harassment, or unauthorized operations against this individual are forbidden. I must order you gentlemen -- (looking straight at Nico) -- with all respect for your work and your courage, to stand down. Lukich shakes his head; Nico is devastated. Jackson takes it all in. Cut To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. POLICE SQUAD ROOM - MORNING\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Opening Close On a desk drawer being opened. Aside from rounds of ammo, notes and an aging eggplant parmigiana sandwich, there are half a dozen hand-labeled audio- cassettes and a small collection of miniaturized bugging devices. notes, hand them to Lieutenant Strozah. Jackson and Lukich watch Nico take out the Above The Law - Rev. 42987 The tapes too\"}, {\"character\": \"LIEUTENANT STROZAH\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"That's my Lawrence Welk collection\"}, {\"character\": \"LIEUTENANT STROZAH\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I want everything you got on this one.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Reluctantly, Nico hands over the tapes. The Lieutenant eyes the bugs and wires\"}, {\"character\": \"LIEUTENANT STROZAH\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I know you don't give a shit about yourself, Toscani.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"But you're gonna put Jackson's ass in a sling, too, with these illegal wires. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 35A. 136A Other Side Of Squad Room Agent Halloran edges up to Jackson, who's grabbing coffee on the far side of the squad room, and watching from there as Nico gives Strozah more of a hard time\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT HALLORAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"What's the story on your partner, Jackson? Did he learn this style or was he born with a brick up his ass?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson checks Halloran out. He's black too and, despite herself, there's a certain rapport\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"He has ethics. Unlike certain others on this case.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Halloran watches the illegal bugs and tapes come out of Nico's drawer\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT HALLORAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"His 'ethics' are gonna cost him his badge and his gun.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"This \\\"white\\\" talk gives Jackson a pain. She slips into her jive mode\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"You don't wanna catch him without no gun.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Halloran's look asks why not\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"'Cause what he do with his hands. make bullet holes look pretty.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Across the room, Nico turns over the tapes. He bad? Bad bad\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT HALLORAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. PRECINCT HOUSE - STAIRWAY - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Jackson come down the stairs. Jackson has had ample excitement for her last week on the force\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Is that enough? Can we do something normal now -- like eat lunch\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Anything you say, Jax. How about Salvano's?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Let it be, Nico. Jackson\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. PRECINCT HOUSE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Jackson's car pulls out into traffic.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. UNMARKED CAR - PARKED \", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson and Nico are eating some fast good. Nico reaches to his jacket pocket; takes out a cassette. What. you kept his tape, too\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Nico already has it in the Player. We hear Fragments of the telephone tap from the body shop in Spanish and English. fully to what appears to be the taped Phone Conversation.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson looks frustrated. Nico listens care- Poetry, ain't it? Nico\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. REAR SALVANO'S RESTAURANT - DAY \", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The pimp comes out and dumps a load of garbage.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. UNMARKED CAR - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Jackson case the restaurant from down the alley.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. REAR SALVANO'S - NICO'S POV - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"From the restaurant door, Salvano and Chi Chi emerge. They get into a black Cadillac and pull out\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"And now for some dessert.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Series Of Shots As Nico's car tails Salvano's through various streets. Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. OAK STREET\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Salvano comes out of a fancy flower shop with a bimbo on his arm. He kisses her goodbye and puts her in a cab\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"And that must be Mrs. Sal. So nice to see married couples still in love.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"144A Nico And Jackson are hidden, waiting. 144B Chi Chi emerges from a dry cleaner's with a suit on a hanger.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. ST. ELIZABETH'S PARISH CHURCH - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Salvano's Caddy pulls up outside the same church where we saw Nico's son get baptized. Salvano and Chi Chi get out, look both ways up and down the street. Salvano, holding flowers, makes eye contact with a car down the block.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. STREET UP BLOCK FROM CHURCH - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico's car backs out of sight around the corner. Sidewalk In Front Of Church Salvano and Chi Chi, seeing nothing, enter the church.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CHURCH - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A smattering of older women and men praying. Salvano and Chi Chi stop at the head of the aisle, genuflect to the altar, move in, take seats toward the front. Back Of Church Nico and Jackson slip in the front door, glide silently into the shadows at the rear of the church\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"This is your mother's church, isn't it\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Yeah. these boys in the choir.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"But I bet she's never seen Nico'S Pov Salvano's head is bowed, but Chi Chi is looking around quite carefully. Nico and Jackson fade into the shadows behind the huge pillars. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 37A. Salvano And Chi Chi After a few moments, the pair rises. They cross them- selves, start out for the front door. As they walk, they continue to look for something.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CHURCH - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Jackson emerge into a courtyard which reveals a day care center and a rectory. They head toward the front of the building. tail on Salvano, is stoped by Nico. He wants to stay and look around. Jackson, planning on picking up their Father Genarro  Nicola! That can't be you in church without the family! Nico turns to see Father Genarro, perspiring in a baggy sweatshirt, a handball glove on his hand. The courtyard alongside the church is marked off as an athletic area. Father Genarro\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"The priest seizes Nico's hand warmly, smiles at Jackson\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"This must be your partner in crime.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I'm Father Genarro. I saw you at the baptismal party. What a partner\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Dolores Jackson\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(smiling, but impatient) Nico, we gotta go -\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"No, please --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"It's good you stopped by. I have to show you something. Please. The priest begins leading Nico and Jackson. Jackson keeps glancing back out the alley to see Salvano's car slowly driving by.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CHURCH BASEMENT - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"This is an old building. The dark corridors resemble an underground bunker. Old trophies and furniture are stored along the walls. The two cops and the priest walk. Another priest emerges from a door, nods, passes. Nico and Jackson glance in through the door as they walk. They reach a door with a broken handle. It looks like a break-in has taken place\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"The rats are getting bigger.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"When did this happen\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Two nights ago. I didn't call the police.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Father Genarro knocks on the door, pauses, then knocks again. he's from Central America stands in the doorway. The door opens. A twelve-year-old who looks like Father Genarro It's all right, son. These are friends. The boy steps back and we Move Into --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CHURCH SANCTUARY - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A largish room, no exposed windows, everything boarded up. Newly-constructed makeshift toilet and shower in one corner, various cots. A number of Latin Refugees -- families mostly -- react shyly as Father Genarro introduces Nico and Jackson. Sister Bonifacia is there, and a youthful priest, Father Tomassino. We will see both of them again\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"These are friends.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"This is Father Tomassino. How do you do\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER TOMASSINO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico shakes the young priest's hand. There is a moment between them as Nico meets Tomassino's eyes, liking what he sees. Genarro, Nico and Jackson take their leave.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The refugees are relieved, however, when Father Nico, Jackson And Father Genarro continue down the hall\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"I didn't know this church was a sanctuary, Father\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"But, perhaps not such a\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Yes. safe one. How long have they been here\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Too long. At least the kids can go to our school.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Who did it, Father\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 41787\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"39A. Kids, maybe\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Maybe worse. It's not the first time\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"We can have a car check by, every hour\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"No. please. Police frighten these people.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CHURCH - MAIN AISLE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The three are outside, taking their leave. A big smile and a hand on Father Genarro's shoulder. The priest is greatly relieved. Really, I don't mind coming by\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Tell me, Nico. When was your last confession\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I'm a married man, Father. I've got no sins to confess\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You're a police officer, you have many sins to confess.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Amen\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Nico and Jackson start off\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You come back Sunday. I feel better when I see Nicola in church.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You don't show, I'm phoning your mother! Dissolve To: Same Church - Pov From Window - Early Morning  High Angle From Across the street: neighborhood people dressed in their Sunday best fill the sidewalk, filing in for Mass. We hear an Organ from inside the church. Various Angles - Congregation An Italian neighborhood becoming more Hispanic. As the churchgoers file in, we see families -- women, kids, babies. Nico, Sara, Rosa And Julian are among the crowd, exchanging pleasantries with friends and neighbors -- in English, Italian and Spanish.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CHURCH - SIDE AISLE\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sara, holding Julian, slips into a pew. As Nico and Rosa follow, Father Genarro passes, heading for the front. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Rosa Father Genarro! I have you to thank for getting my son back into church\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"It's amazing what shame can accomplish.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Father Genarro smiles and continues on toward the pulpit. Quick Dissolve To\"}, {\"character\": \"VARIOUS SHOTS\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A)\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The Choir building to the finish of a hymn. B) Nico'S Wife  also singing, balancing baby Julian and a hymnbook. C) Nico And His Mother Rosa sing with full gusto. D) The Choir Master makes the sign to be seated. E\"}, {\"character\": \"CONGREGATION\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"We notice a young, intellectual-looking man\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"sits. wearing wire-rim glasses, sitting in the front row. We will see his face again later. He looks out of place and glances around, surprised as. F) Father Genarro moves into the pulpit, opens his Bible\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER GENARRO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"In nomine patris, filius et spiritu sancti. \"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sara And Julian The little one starts to Cry; she comforts him. Nico reaches over to try to help. The Baby continues Fussing. Nico looks toward the priest and the front of the church. He notices a woman in a black shawl rise from the front of the church and turn, heading down one of the side aisles\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Way to go, Julian -- perfect timing.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(examines Julian's diaper) Above The Law - Rev. 42987 She cynically smiles at Nico. Nico sees the woman in black pass toward the exit of the church. Closeup - Woman It is the same woman Nico and Jackson were following with Abandano, the lawyer! Closeup - Large Shopping Bag The woman has left it in front of the votive candles directly before the priest's pulpit. Closeup - Nico His head spins from the shopping bag to the doorway -- Nico'S Pov - Doorway The woman is hastily sneaking out. Back To Nico Instantly he pushes his family to the floor, covering them with his body. Closeup - Nico - Second Later A Powerful Explosion erupts between the priest Boom!!! and his congregation. Fragments of plaster, wood, and marble come blasting past Nico and his family! Churchgoers in the first rows are blown off their feet by the shock wave of the blast. Pews overturn, smoke everywhere -- Choir is shrieking hysterically. Stone and plaster dust rain down on them from the ceiling. Congregation is in total pandemonium. Screams, cries, panic -- Pulpit has been blown to oblivion. Where Father Genarro had been standing is now nothing but smoke and rubble\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Prone, covering Sara and the baby, groping frantically to protect his mother as well\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"We're okay! We're okay!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico checks them and his mother swiftly. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Rosa Help the others! Help them, Nico! Statue Of Jesus Splattered with real blood. Angle On COnGREGATIOn Cut To: Cut Back To: Everyone is down, reeling from the concussion, dust and smoke. Nico rises alone from this scene\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Help each other move outside. Be calm.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. SIDE OF CHURCH - MORNING\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"From a doorway and a shattered window smoke pours forth. We hear Screams from inside.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CHURCH\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico on his feet, plainly the leader in this moment of terror. him toward the door. Nico grabs a stout-looking church- goer. Worshippers, shattered and bleeding, pour past Nico Call 911. Tell 'em to send everything they got! Sara, get the baby and Mama outside. Nico starts for the altar where the damage is worst.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. FRONT OF CHURCH - MORNING\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The congregation streams out in terror-stricken disarray. We see Nico's family -- they're all right. Nico appears from the church, carrying a young choir girl. He hands the child over to two older women, races back into the church. Long Shot - Street Outside Church The first paramedic van comes speeding around the corner\"}, {\"character\": \"SIREN BLARING.\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Police cars appear right behind --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CHURCH\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico appears through the backlit smoke and kneels over the bloodied body of Father Genarro. He desperately tries to maintain the priest's life. Cut To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. HOSPITAL/ICU WARD - AFTERNOON\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The aftermath of the blast. Doctors and nurses have the scene more of less under control, but there's still plenty of pain and misery.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. HOSPITAL ROOM - AFTERNOON\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico stands, his back to the wall -- a scary, blank look on his face. plugs on the terribly mutilated body of Father Genarro. A nun is crying; a fellow priest is blessing the Father. A doctor and several nurses are pulling the Jackson arrives. Nico talks to her, aside\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I want a list of everyone that's been treated here today. Everyone.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Right\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Then find those sanctuary people, the ones we saw in the church basement --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"As Jackson makes notes\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Find out where they're from, why anyone would want to harm them.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson flips her notepad shut, ready to go. Where are you gonna be\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Just stay near a radio. I'll find you.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. HOSPITAL CORRIDOR - NICO'S MOTHER  - AFTERNOON\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sits on a bench with a bandage over one eye. Sara and Julian are sleeping beside her. Nico kneels beside his mother, deeply concerned. Nico takes his mother's arm, helps her to her feet. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 She begins sobbing softly. Other members of Sara wakes and picks up Julian. Mama knows Father Genarro has died. the congregation are in the hallway, mourning. Nico, with his family, takes several steps toward the exit. Suddenly, Nico stops. He sees Agent Neeley entering (the Fbi man who ordered him off the case) accompanied by Lieutenant Strozah and two uniformed officers\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Sara. go down to the car; I'll be with you in a minute.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He hails Neeley. I need to talk to you. Nico (a glance to Strozah and others) . Alone. Neeley nods. fire exit door -- Nico leads him off the corridor, through a Stairwell Landing The door closes behind them. Nico and the Fbi man are alone on the stairway landing\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"What the hell is it, Toscani?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Without warning, Nico grabs Neeley by both lapels, slams him furiously into the wall! You\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"That's what the hell it is!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Get your goddam hands off me\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Neeley tries to shake free; Nico won't let him.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You let Salvano walk\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Salvano?! Are you crazy?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"What does he have to do with this\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"That was no cherry bomb in there. That was C-fucking-4!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(struggles to master his rage) I've used that shit. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Nico  I know what it smells like, I know what it blows like -- Neeley glares at Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Salvano never came near that C-4. It's in federal holding now! Besides, why would he blow up a church\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I tailed Salvano. Two days ago. Him and one of his apes were in that church -- and they weren't taking communion. I saw some broad saw who was with his lawyer plant the bomb. Now I want some goddamn answers\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You tailed him? After I ordered you off?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Where is he? Where's Salvano\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"My orders were release him. Not babysit him.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Neeley brushes Nico's fingermarks off his lapels\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You think you're rough stuff, Toscani -- martial arts hero, chop suey crap. Well I'll tell you something: you're not bullet- proof. You're not even a good cop.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(composes himself; reclaims his dignity) You sneak around, playing your street dick games. But all you come up with is conjecture, wild coincidence and bullshit\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I want the agent who signed for the explosives.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I'll do my job. You do yours\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Bank on it, pal\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 41787\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico stalks off. The door slams. Cut To: Montage With Score A)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. \\\"BOGOTA\\\"  - LATE AFTERNOON\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico's unmarked car whips in front. Nico storms toward the front door of the restaurant. B)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. RESTAURANT - LATE AFTERNOON\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico storms through toward the restaurant rear. The employees are getting ready for the evening crowd. He flashes his badge, checks the kitchen, Salvano's office. The man is gone. C)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. MORGUE - LATE AFTERNOON\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson has her list from the hospital. A coroner and his assitant show her a body on a slab. The body is that of Alan Singletary, the man we saw in the front row of the church. Jackson takes notes. The dead man is definitely not the ethnic type you'd expect in St. Mary's congregation. D)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. BODY AND FENDER SHOP - LATE AFTERNOON\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The same place where Nico and Jackson wire-tapped Chi Chi. All shake their head, gesture emphatically. Salvano not here. Nico interrogates the shop boss, several workers. E) Cut Back To Morgue - Jackson takes Polaroids of the dead man's I.D. and personal effects. Closeup Of Dead Man'S Effects as Jackson's flash pops. We see clearly a U.S. Senate staff Id, a U.S. Senate office building parking pass and an Illinois driver's license with address.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. AFFLUENT BROWNSTONE - LATE AFTERNOON\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico comes storming out. A Maid and a bodyguard follow after him screaming. The door slams. We see it is missing a panel\"}, {\"character\": \"MAID\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You gonna be in real trouble, mister, when El Senor Salvano find out about dis.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. ST. ELIZABETH'S CHURCH - LATE AFTERNOON\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson at the blast scene. Police tapes rope the area off while a Tv news crew photographs the damage. Jackson talks with neighborhood people, asking questions.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. BICEK'S BAR - LATE AFTERNOON\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico in the alley, grilling several tough guys we saw be- fore when he raided this bar. The answers are all zero; Nico's disgusted, worn out, frustrated. He starts out the alley -- At the edge of the street, a battered van pulls in. rette in his mouth. As Nico approaches, turning toward his car -- A jacketed Latino Man leans against it, an unlit ciga\"}, {\"character\": \"FIRST LATINO\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"'Cuse me, sir. Can I bum a light?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico slows, eyeing the guy dubiously. As he reaches to his jacket -- The side door of the van flashes open. A .38 is leveled straight at Nico's head. Instantly three other Latino hoods leap to the sidewalk\"}, {\"character\": \"FIRST LATINO\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Don't even think about it, motherfucker.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Machete Man snatches Nico's gun from its shoulder holster. Two hoods shove Nico back into the alley. them. Nico checks out his assailants quickly. Four of Machete, Crowbar, Ball Bat, Gun\"}, {\"character\": \"MACHETE MAN\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You come to our streets. fuck with our people. Now our people gonna fuck with you.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The five advance on Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"PIPE MAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"We ain't gonna shoot you, man. We gonna beat you to death. You gonna learn what it means to 'get down.\"}, {\"character\": \"QUICK CUTS\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A)\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico is trapped. The hoods advancing. Nico has a moment of stillness, as if all senses are clicking out of normal gear and into some hyper-combat readi- ness. Then: B) C) D) E) F) G) Gun and Machete Man are side by side. As Machete Man starts to move, Nico spins in beside him, seizes his wrist, twists it violently, wrenching the machete away, keeping Machete Man between him and Gun Man so Gun Man can't shoot. In a flash, Nico swings the machete, slicing over the top of Machete Man, half-severing the wrist of Gun Man. Gun Man falls, clutching his wrist in agony; the gun skitters away beneath a chain link fence, out of reach. Nico flips Machete Man sending him crash- ing, half-unconscious. Instantly, Pipe Man aims a home run shot at Nico's head. Nico uses the machete, matches the angle of the oncoming blow, slides under and, in the same arc, blocks the blow and turns it into a strike, slashing Pipe Man's tendons behind the knee. Pipe Man goes down on one knee, writhing, hamstrung, crying out in pain. Now Ball Bat attacks. Nico intercepts the blow, flips Bat Man ass over teakettle, sending him sail- ing -- feet first -- through the side window of the van. just his head and shoulders dangling free. Bat Man Crashes Through the Glass, hung up with Nico is spread out, feet wide, in a crouch. Crowbar Man sees his chance. He is the fiercest of the four, and the savviest fighter. He throws three consecu- tive vicious blows at Nico's head; Nico drops to one knee, dodges the blows, then intercepts the third, machete in hand, matches the arc of interception and whips the blade up -- straight into the crotch of Crowbar Man. mains frozen a moment, staring at Nico, then down at his own groin. Crowbar Man can't believe it. He re- Machete Man, the first to be flipped, struggles des- perately to regain his senses. He tries to get Nico's gun from his own pocket, but Nico bats it a- way. Machete Man scrambles to his feet, in terror, bolts. Nico snatches his gun from the sidewalk, glances to Bat Man who is still half-dangling from the van window. head, then tears off after Machete Man -- Nico gives Bat Man one parting punch to the\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. STREET - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Shrieks from passersby as Machete Man hurtles past, straight into the street. A car nearly hits him, he vaults its hood. too leaps the car, whose owner is staring, cursing -- Here comes Nico, in hot pursuit. He Angle Down Block An all-out foot face. Machete Man is a speedster; he hurdles a row of trash cans. Two Young Girls, on a stoop, whistle as he passes. Fly, baby\"}, {\"character\": \"FIRST GIRL\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"tears after this human cannonball. Amazingly, he's gaining --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. BODEGA - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Machete Man highballs off the sidewalk, straight into a Mom and Pop groceria. Customers scatter in shock as the hood blasts past them, out the back door. Here comes Nico. Patrons curse in Spanish as he barrels past --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. YARD BEHIND BODEGA - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Machete Man bolts from the bodega into a small patio with tables and chairs. He leaps the fence into the next yard, which belongs to a funeral home. He hurdles the headstone inventory, clambers up the fence on the far side -- Back To Nicco pursuing along the same route. Machete Man claws his way to the top of the fence and onto a frame- work of two-by-fours which form an arbor-like canopy a- bove the third back yard. Plastic sheeting is tacked between the beams. Machete Man glances back at Nico, starts out -- tightrope-style -- across the two-by-fours. Nico reaches the fence behind the hood, starts also onto the two-by-fours. We hear Female Screams from below as the rickety structure starts to wobble precariously. Machete Man reaches the far side. A fire escape is ad- jacent; he grabs for it, starts up. Nico catches him by the ankle. The two crash together back onto the two-by- fours, which give way, sending them plunging into -- Backyard Of Flower Shop - Day Four young Oriental women, potting plants, react with terror as the two bodies Crash through. Machete Man scrambles away from Nico but is trapped in the corner next to the rear shop door. The flower girls can't move either; Nico and the hood are too near the door. The girls retreat to the far corner, squealing in fright\"}, {\"character\": \"MACHETE MAN\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"No, hermano. Please --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico starts menacingly toward the hood, breathing hard from the chase. Who put up the money\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"What money\"}, {\"character\": \"MACHETE MAN\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico grabs him by the hair.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You didn't come after me for a piece of ass. (twists the youth's Nico neck) Who paid you? I told ya! No one\"}, {\"character\": \"MACHETE MAN\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico slams him with a fierce shot to the ribs. The hood doubles over, gasping. The flower girls shriek even louder.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico turns to the girls with a ferocious glare\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Shut up!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The girls instantly go silent in terror. Nico turns back to Machete Man, spins him violently face-down, jacking the punk's right arm straight out behind him. We see that Nico can break his elbow with one blow\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Give it to me!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico raises his fist to strike. Jimmy Constanza\"}, {\"character\": \"MACHETE MAN\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico shoves the hood into the ground, tearing the hood's wallet from his trouser pocket. Nico rips the wallet a- part, seizes the kid's identification and holds it up. grabs the punk by the hair with his free hand. Machete Man is staring up in terror, wondering what this means.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He Nico If you're lying to me, I'll come and kill you right in your own fucking kitchen. Nico dumps him on the ground and walks away. Instantly Machete Man changes his tune. Salvano! Bautista Salvano\"}, {\"character\": \"MACHETE MAN\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico walks back, his foot smashes into the punk's face. He hits the ground with a thud\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Gracias, muchacho.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico walks away. Montage With Score A)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. NICO'S HOUSE - KITCHEN - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico at the kitchen table spread with notepads, old add- ress books, 3X5 cards. He's on the phone, impatient, apparently getting nowhere. He slams the phone down. B)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. LIVING ROOM - EVENING\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico paces, phone cradled to ear, talking urgently. Click: he's been hung up on; he looks at the receiver in frustration and disgust. C) Close - Corkboard On Kitchen Wall Nico's hands pushpin a 3X5 card into the wall. D) Insert - 3X5 Card We read: \\\"Fbi Agent Smith 11:53 B.S. Covering for who?\\\" E) Kitchen - Night Nico back at the table, listening to the wiretap tape, transcribing it. F) Another Angle - Kitchen - Night  Nico holds Julian, goes over notes. G) Close - Yellow Legal Pad The page is headed: \\\"Father Genarro.\\\" Below in doodle formation, are a series of boxes, each one containing a phrase. We read: \\\"Father G had some- thing on Salvano?\\\" \\\"Church break-in?\\\" \\\"Drug infor- mation?\\\" Nico's pencil crosses everything out. \\\"Father G connected to Fbi?\\\" Irritably\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Appears in a nightgown at the kitchen doorway. She looks frail, frightened. Music Ends I can't sleep. Will you come and hold me?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Nico Of course I will. I've been waiting to hear from Jax. She was supposed to get back to me by now.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. NICO'S BEDROOM - LATE NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico comes in with his arms around Sara. She stops near the bed, holds him tight. They look to little Julian sleeping in the crib nearby\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Thank God you couldn't find your shoes. sitting in the front row.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"We would of have been Alright, I know the rules -- I don't ask you don't tell. But could've died today and I deserve to know. Why did we go to church this morning\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I'm willing to break the rules; I'm willing to tell you whatever I know. But I need some time. Could you just give me some time?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico leans to kiss her, but is cut off by the Harsh Ring of a Phone. glance at each other -- Sara starts at the sound. She and Nico I'll bet that's her\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Nico picks up the phone\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"This better be good, Jax\"}, {\"character\": \"MAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"It's bad, Nico.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico glances to Sara. The voice on the phone is not Jackson. his lips. the exact time. \\\"Two-fifteen.\\\" Nico is chilled. He glances to Sara, finger to Sara, not sure what's going on, mouths: He points to his bare wrist as if wanting to know Nico Long time, Nelson. Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. STREET - PHONE BOOTH - LATE NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"We recognize Fox, Nico's buddy from Se Asia whom we met in the opening sequence. Fox, too, of course, looks 15 years older. We are unable to identify from where Fox calls. He wears a suit and seems quite prosperous\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You should know not to use a name on an open line.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I'm gonna talk for fifteen seconds, then I'm getting off. You're in trouble, Nico. Back To Nico'S Bedroom - Late Night Fox  Serious, serious trouble. Take your wife and family and get them someplace safe now. Back To Street - Phone Booth - Late Night Fox You hear me? Now. I'm risking my ass by telling you this. Good luck, kid. Back To Nico'S Bedroom - Late Night The Phone Clicks Dead. Nico tries to keep a casual ex- pression. Sara sees through it -- she knows he's shaken\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"That was Fox, wasn't it?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico doesn't answer\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Why is the C.I.A. calling you at two in the morning\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"It's okay, sweetheart --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(crosses to her, puts his arms around her) -- You know what a crazy bastard Fox is. He gets drunk and forgets he's halfway around the world. He calls me. Nico gives her a squeeze and a smile. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Nico He just wanted to make sure we got his Christmas card.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. BEDROOM - LATER\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sara is sleeping next to Nico. Julian next to her. A Loud Pounding comes O.S. from the front door. Nico jumps out of bed. he steps quickly to the front window, looks out -- His gun appears in his hand, as if from nowhere, Nico'S Pov - Street Below Two unmarked cars pull in. Back To Nico He moves swiftly to the rear window and spots another un- marked car.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. DOWNSTAIRS - FRONT DOOR\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico enters the vestibule in his pajama bottoms with his gun in his hand. F.B.I., Toscani. Open up\"}, {\"character\": \"VOICE THROUGH DOOR \", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico pulls aside a curtained glass panel; he recognizes two uniformed police officers, plus Neeley and Halloran, the Fbi agents who authorized the release of Salvano. He lowers his gun, opens the door. The cops surge in\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"It's a little early for breakfast, O'Hara\"}, {\"character\": \"O'HARA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sorry, Nico.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You're under arrest. Agent Neeley (reaches for Nico's gun) I'll take this, thank you. Before Neeley can get his hand on the gun, Nico, without pausing, hands it over to another agent\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"No, you won't. I'm gonna give it to you.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. NICO'S BEDROOM - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Julian Bawls fearfully; Sara holds him, trembling. Nico is hurriedly getting dressed. A cop and the Fbi agents stand at the door\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"This is ridiculous -- there's no need for this!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"It's all right, darling\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Two agents enter the room carrying Nico's confiscated papers and tapes and begin rummaging through dressers, jewelry boxes and closets. Rosa crosses swiftly to calm Sara\"}, {\"character\": \"ROSA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Who do you think you are -- coming in here like this, treating my son like a criminal\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Why are you terrifying us? There's an infant here!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico pulls on a jacket. He looks like he could kill. He restrains himself for his family's sake\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT HALLORAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Check that coat.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The cops cross to frisk Nico. Sara, still holding the baby, starts slapping at them. Get your hands off him\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Rosa grabs Sara --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico (to Sara, allowing himself to be frisked) It's all a mistake, Sara -- It's gonna be all right. The cops steer Nico toward the door\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"The Police Association's got lawyers for this, you bastards!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Sara grabs for the phone; Nico is manhandled out the door --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. NICO'S HOUSE - LATE NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The neighbors are now on their porches. Nico is led to a waiting unmarked car. Cut To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. POLICE HEADQUARTERS - LATE NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Bad Dude, the bartender we remember from Nico's first visit to the Polish bar, finishes signing a deposition. A cop takes the paper. Bad Dude stands, glances half- fearfully, half-defiantly to Nico, who is led down a hall- way flanked by two uniformed officers. Agent Halloran opens the door for Bad Dude, who exits.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. INTERROGATION ROOM - LATE NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Neeley, Halloran, Lieutenant Strozah and Deputy Superinten- dent Jack Crowder. Halloran indicates a stack of depositions, tapes and notes on the table before Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT HALLORAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Illegal wiretaps. Unauthorized surveillance.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"When were you born, asshole\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Associating with known felons. Disobeying direct orders --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Where's Jackson\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"She's outa this\"}, {\"character\": \"CROWDER\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT HALLORAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You're the rotten apple in this barrel, Toscani. We don't have to look any farther than you and your 'family.'\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico comes out of his chair, going for Halloran. Strozah tries to block him, but it's useless\"}, {\"character\": \"LIEUTENANT STROZAH\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You damn fool! You wanna\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico! go to prison?! Nico stops. toward Halloran like a loaded gun. He's speechless with rage. His finger points Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Crowder (indicates more depositions) Unlawful entry. Illegal search and seizure -\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You'll never build a frame on this chickenshit\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You were ordered to back off on Salvano. But you had too big a hard-on for that, didn't you--\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico contains his fury. He steps away from Strozah, with a gesture that says \\\"I won't hurt you.\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You can't be in on this.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Fred. Nico faces his lieutenant -- a look that calls on long years of comradeship and loyalty. Strozah is torn. He's a good man, over his head in a situation he doesn't com- pletely understand\"}, {\"character\": \"LIEUTENANT STROZAH\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You're officially suspended, Toscani. I want your tin. and your iron.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Neeley leans past Nico; drops Nico's gun (with an evidence tag on it) onto the table. Nico looks to Strozah, who averts his eyes. Nico flips his badge onto the table. You holding me\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You can walk for now. But don't walk far.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Cut To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. PHONE BOOTH ON DOWNTOWN STREET - DAWN\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"We are outside of a cop breakfast hangout. Several police cars are parked in the lot. Nico is on the phone. Sara, I'm okay. I love you\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Cut To:\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987 58A. 215A\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. NICO'S KITCHEN\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sara on the phone\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Where are you? Why aren't you coming home?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Cut To: 215B\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. PHONE BOOTH\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico I'll be home later. Lukich will be there. Tell mama not to worry. Jackson and Lukich are waiting by Nico's car. They see Nico emerge from the phone booth. Cut To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. STREET - NICO, JACKSON AND LUKICH - DAWN\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A mood of urgency. -- I found the sanctuary people\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 41787\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson  They're refugees from El Salvador, Guatemala, Chile. They won't talk to me, they're terrified of cops. Jackson has an armload of notes, including photocopies of news clippings\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Ready for this? One of the people killed at the church was definitely not a congregation member.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"She shows Nico and Lukich the Polaroids we saw her take in the morgue\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Alan Singletary. He's an aide to Senator Harrison.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico is electrified\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"That's right. Harrison. Foreign relations committee. The guy who's been crawling all over the Central American drug connections\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You're gonna make a helluva D.A., Jax.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"God help us. Lukich (savors the com- pliment\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"I've been at the Tribune all night, wearing out their Xerox machine. Harrison's staff has been compiling some kind of white paper. next week.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He's due to release it Nico's mind races. That's how Fox knew\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"What\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Nico turns to Lukich, dead earnest.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Nico I want you to go to my Luke. house. has the number. Get my family ready to move out. Call Branca. my mother You got it, buddy\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Stay with 'em. We'll be there\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"What's going on, Nico? What happened\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I got a call last night. An old agency friend. He told me my family was in danger.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jax and Lukich can't put all the pieces together yet. But if it's drugs-Cia-Senate, it's got to be heavy. You got a weapon\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Lukich knows he doesn't. He glances up and down the street, makes sure no one's watching -- then cracks the driver's door of his car. There's a bulge in the map pocket.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico pulls out a Sig Saur .45. Try this on\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Jackson watches Luke slip Nico a clip.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. DAY CARE CENTER  - MORNING\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Cut To: Opening Close On the faces of the sanctuary refugees. They are faces that have known fear and tragedy. The kind of faces we see on newsreels after villages have been burned and family members murdered. The refugees have been moved from church basement to a back room in the day care center. background. we saw in Genarro's hospital room) watch over the people. Nico is frustrated; he can't crack the refugees' fear. A nun and a priest (whom Nico kneels, facing them. Jackson in the Nico Sister. you know me. Tell them there's no need for fear\"}, {\"character\": \"SISTER BONIFACIA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"There is rubble all over the yard, Nicola.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(The Rest Of The Scene May Be In English, Or Spanish With Subtitles, At The DIRECTOr'S Discretion.\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I was there. in the church. They tried to kill my family, too.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Several of the refugees look like they want to speak, but they are terrified\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I know there was a man here, from an American senator's office. Who was he going to speak to?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The refugees become increasingly anxious\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Was it you, senora?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Was it you? More silence. Glances among the people. Finally: The priest\"}, {\"character\": \"REFUGEE WOMAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The others shrink. The Woman glances to them\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Who?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Father Genarro? The other one\"}, {\"character\": \"REFUGEE WOMAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico looks to the American priest standing there The young one. From Costa\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"No. Rica. Sister Bonifacia sighs. Father Tomassino\"}, {\"character\": \"SISTER BONIFACIA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson has her pad out, taking notes. Bonifacia knows too much has already been revealed; she must speak He came alone. two weeks ago. He had papers. Papers to give to the senator.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico tries to contain his excitement; not scare anyone by losing his calm\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"But the bomb. The bomb was planted to destroy the pulpit\"}, {\"character\": \"SISTER BONIFACIA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Father Tomassino was going to give the Mass that day.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Father Genarro talked him out of it. The refugees' faces confirm this\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"It was Father Tomassino they were trying to kill.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Bonifacia starts softly to cry. Nico puts his hand on her shoulder, comforting her\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Where is Tomassino? Where is he now?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The nun shakes her head. Nico looks to the refugees. They don't know, either\"}, {\"character\": \"REFUGEE MAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He run, mister. He go --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He gestures: \\\"who knows where?\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"If you know where he is, you've got to tell me. I want to help him.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I can help him. The refugees lower their eyes. Bonifacia continues her soft weeping. \\\"Enough, let's leave these poor people alone.\\\" Nico stands, touches Bonifacia one more time on the shoulder -- Nico glances to Jackson; her look says\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. CHURCH DAY CARE BUILDING - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Jackson come out. Nico has made a decision. You're outa this, Jax. Go home\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson You see this list? Well, I'm not done. Nico admires his partner's guts, but he's worried\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"I'm not a rookie, Toscani. Now, go home. Get your family out of here.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico agrees. The pair starts to split. Nico (calls after Jackson) Just paperwork, you understand?\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. NICO'S CAR - MOVING - MORNING\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico drives, a jumble of emotions on his face. Urgency fear, exhaustion. He's deep in thought --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. INTERSECTION - MORNING\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Cut To: Nico's car pulls up at a stop light. He looks around without really seeing. An old lady pulls a shopping cart while a crossing guard takes some kids across the street\"}, {\"character\": \"ANOTHER CAR\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Roars up out of nowhere, without two men inside, Screech- Ing to a stop head-on to Nico's door. Its doors spring open --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico dives toward his own passenger door -- Second Car - Two More Armed Men leap out, Open Fire with pistols and automatic weapons\"}, {\"character\": \"QUICK CUTS\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico's car riddled with a furious Fusillade. Windows Blow Out; the driver's door is shredded --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Nico - On Floorboard crawling frantically; shoving the passenger door open as a Firestorm of lead and Flying Glass Blazes all around him\"}, {\"character\": \"FOUR MEN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Firing point blank into Nico's car. The men are cool, professional.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico spills from the passenger door onto the ground, scrambles like mad under his own car toward one of the attackers' cars. Pedestrians Around Intersection scream and scatter in terror\"}, {\"character\": \"FOUR MEN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Firing as shells spew from the ejection ports of their weapons.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico'S Car being chewed to pieces -- Nico - Under Men'S Car crawling at full speed from the car's front to its back. On the ground, alongside the car, spent Cartridge Cases Rain like hailstones\"}, {\"character\": \"FOUR MEN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"As their magazines empty. The last shells spring free, Gun Barrels Sizzle, blue smoke fills the air. The leader waves two men forward to check their kill. At that instant:\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico springs to his feet behind the men, the Sig Saur .45 clutched in both hands. (He has crawled under both cars to envelop his attackers.) Over here, you sons-a-bitches\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico's rage is superhuman. The men stare in conster- nation. his weapon --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"One of the men has a fresh magazine half into Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Nico (eyes like an animal) Try it. Be my guest. The man lets the magazine clatter to the street. The others raise their hands. It takes all Nico's strength to keep from wasting all four of them on the spot. His gaze swings wildly around the intersection. He spots a corner grocery store. A phone inside\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Over there! Move it! -- Now!!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The men are scared shitless. They put their hands in back of their heads; trot jelly-legged --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CORNER GROCERY STORE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A Pakistani counter clerk takes one look at the mob enter- ing his store and bolts for the rear. A customer exits as Nico herds his captives in. Hands on the counter\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Three men do it; the fourth is slow.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Don't tempt me, Asshole -\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"The fourth obeys. Nico moves to the pay phone on the wall, covering the men with his .45. He grabs the re- ceiver in his free hand; tries to dial. Adrenaline makes his hand shake; the dials spin wrong -- One of the men sees Nico's dilemma. To hit 911, Nico has to take his eye momentarily off his captives. As Nico turns again to the dial -- A free-standing sales display hurtles toward him, crashing into his gun hand. One of the men has lunged into the display; now he dives atop Nico a second later. into a glass freezer. Somehow Nico gets to his feet. One of the men grabs Nico's gun; Nico swings one of the freezer doors -- Wham! -- smack into the man's face. The Glass Shatters; the man drops like a rock. Now it's three against one -- prime odds for Nico. He wades into his attackers. into a makeup display. One fool is lucky enough to land a blow that bloodies Nico's nose; he pays with a shattered forearm and a head-first heave into an ice cream locker --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A coffee stand goes flying. A body sails The whole human pile crashes, thundering Pov From Outside Store It looks like a tornado has hit the interior. Magazine Racks Crash, mayo jars fly through the air, the Ice Machine seems to Explode as a man's back careens into it -- Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Street Corner Up Block Two police cars heave into view, Sirens Wailing -- Front Doors Of Store Nico takes the last man, lifts him up, and drives him like a battering ram straight through the glass\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Wild-eyed and bloody, sees the cop cars whipping into the corner. away to race for. He bolts down a gangway.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He spins to see his .45 on the floor -- too far Cut To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. NICO'S HOUSE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The Phone Rings next to Lukich. Sara starts towards it. Lukich stops her with a look; he picks up the phone\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Yeah?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Intercut Nico On Street - PHOnE Booth - Day Nico Get their stuff into the car now. Do it in the alley, not the driveway. I'll be there in five minutes. Cut To: Two More Police Cars Squealing around a corner, entering the block where Nico is. Nico - On Sidewalk Lets them pass, keeping low. He sprints across the street and down the alley. Omitted\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. NICO'S BEDROOM - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Cut To: Sara grabs a handful of dresses from the closet and angrily throws them into an open suitcase on the bed. Nico watches, hoping to ride the storm. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Sara Your job and your family in one day, Nico. You're batting a thousand\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Sara.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sara is at the dresser, pulling open drawers, dumping her clothes haphazardly into the suitcase. She stops suddenly. She pulls out a handgun and ammo from her panty drawer. starts to weep. around her. Nico steps up behind her, puts his arms She Nico You'll be safe with Uncle Branca. It's gotta be this way. I'm sorry. He turns her around to face him\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Don't you think I'd rather be with you?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He holds her passionately. Rosa coughs loudly in the doorway. Sara -- Mama. you got your medicine? Don't forget the baby's sweater -- I know about babies\"}, {\"character\": \"ROSA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"We glimpse other relatives in the hallway; Nico hands them a pair of suitcases; they hurry off --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sara (of Nico's bloodied shirt) You sure you're all right? I am if you are\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Don't worry --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"We needed a vacation, anyway. Sara takes her suitcase, hurries out --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. ALLEY BEHIND NICO'S HOUSE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Branca's sedan is half-loaded; Branca adds a few more bags. Lukich's car is parked behind it. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 67A\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I'll give you five minutes start. We have to do it this way.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(crossing yard with Sara) They get their suitcases into the sedan. Mama and the baby are already aboard. Sara gets into the passenger seat. Lukich comes around from the front, glancing around like a lookout. Where's Jax\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"She thinks there may be documents at some guy's apartment.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico starts toward the rear basement door. Lukich falls in with him.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. BASEMENT - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Lukich enter, start down the steps. They killed the wrong priest\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Lukich doesn't understand There was a second priest. from Costa Rica. hiding at the church. He was the one they meant to kill.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico starts to remove a large piece of ducting from the basement heater. And you know where to find him\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"No\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"The hole in the foundation holds several shotguns and a couple of pistols, some passports and some cash.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You're gonna need help\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico grabs the pistols, starts to strap them on.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Just stay with my family Nico Nico replaces the piece of foundation, starts back up the steps. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 What are you gonna do\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You don't want to know.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. ALLEY BEHIND NICO'S HOUSE\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Branca Starts the Sedan. Sara looks back, pained. Rosa, Lukich and Julian are also in the car. Nico grabs another hand-carried case from the basement, hurries into Lukich's car. Nico'S Pov - Looking Down Driveway Two police cars pull up to the front of the house. High Angle Shot - Alley Behind House Lukich's car continues off. Cut To: 250A\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. SUBURBAN HOUSE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"We see Uncle Branca's car and Lukich's car out front.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. SAFE HOUSE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Branca leads Nico, Sara, Rosa, Julian and Lukich down a corridor. basement rec room. Two older Italian women open a door leading to a Branca My sister's cousin's place. You're safe -- not even I can find this joint. The family enters the back room. They take in their sanctuary. Cut To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. PARKING LOT - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Agent Neeley hurries across the lot toward his car. He gets in, Starts the Engine. As he puts the car in gear -- Barrel Of .45 Automatic nestles behind his right ear\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Don't forget your seat belt.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. FEDERAL WAREHOUSE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico walks casually beside Agent Neeley, holding his gun out of sight in his pocket. They proceed down a corridor. hind them we glimpse a security checkpoint, manned by two uniformed guards, through which they apparently have already passed. Be- Angle - Corridor The two walk past floor-to-ceiling warehouse shelves, packed with labeled boxes, film cans, etc. which are visible through a heavy wire-mesh screen\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Congratulations, Toscani. You just made number four on the most wanted list.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 41787 69A. Nico -- I'm bucking for number one. Keep walking -- Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Administrative Window A pot-bellied, Naval-retired-type Clerk looks up from his desk as Nico and Neeley come up to the counter. We see a sign: \\\"Evidence Holding Depot -- You Must Have Your Requi- sition Number!!!\\\" The Clerk stands, chomping a cigar, wad- dles to the counter. We see his arms covered with tattoos. What can I do for you, lads\"}, {\"character\": \"CLERK\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Neeley presents his Id\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"There was a quantity of C-4 explosive brought in four days ago --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Hell, that's gone\"}, {\"character\": \"CLERK\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"When\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"CLERK\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Right away, pardner. They scooped that stuff outa here before we even got it tagged.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Who\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Who took it\"}, {\"character\": \"CLERK\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"C.I.A.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico reacts, nudges Neeley once more\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"We'd like to see the paperwork.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The Clerk has an accordion file right under the counter. He indicates a sign-in book. You gotta sign\"}, {\"character\": \"CLERK\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Neeley signs the book. The Clerk starts leafing through his files, searching for the release form Yeah. I remember that guy. Flew in special from Langley. Bomb tech. Real nice fella --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(finds the form, lifts it from file) -- Here it is. Fox. Nelson Fox. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Nico snatches the release form. Stares at the signature, stunned.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. LAKEFRONT - DESERTED SECTION - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Neeley's car parked in the boondocks along the lake. Female  -- Here it is, sir. Coming in from Langley now --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CAR\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Neeley holds the radio mike, as if about to say something. Nico shoves his gun against the guy's temple. Female  -- That agent has been with the Central American desk, uh, since '84 -\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Thank you. That's what I wanted.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico takes the mike, clicks it back into its cradle. Neeley freezes, unsure what Nico's going to do with him\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Dump your shoes. Ditch your I.D. on the floor.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico watches the Fbi man obey\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"So you think I'm a lousy cop, huh, Neeley? Maybe I am. But I haven't got my face buried up Washington's ass.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nobody buys me, Toscani\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Yeah? Then somebody pulled the plug on your brain, pal. You didn't come up with the second priest, did you? Or Harrison's dead aide.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(as Neeley fumbles with his laces) Hurry up! You heard the radio. The Agency's pushing buttons and bodies are dropping like flies. You assholes are missing half the case! Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Despite his animosity toward Nico, Neeley is beginning to realize this cop is onto something. Listen. Toscani -\"}, {\"character\": \"AGENT NEELEY\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico grabs Neeley's shoes, heaves them into the back seat. He shoves the agent out the door, swings himself behind the wheel.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Watch your step. Nico\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. DESERTED LAKEFRONT - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico drives off, leaving the Fbi man miles from nowhere. Cut To: Montage with Score and V.O. A)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. POLICE HEADQUARTERS - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"From out of an elevator and down a busy corridor march the brass, Deputy Superintendent Crowder included. Lieutenant Strozah lags slightly behind. They enter an auditorium where a large contingent of press, cameras ready, wait. B)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CONDO COMPLEX - HALLWAY - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson outside an apartment door in a Yuppie-esque condo complex. She looks both ways to be safe, then slides a credit card behind the lock. The door opens. C)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. CONVENTION CENTER - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico parks Neeley's car in a huge packed lot. A towering marquee sign reads: \\\"Computer Expo '87.\\\" Nico starts on foot toward the convention center entrance. D)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CONDO APARTMENT - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson enters, looking guilty as hell. She picks up a framed photo from a piano: the dead Senator's aide posed smiling beside a distinguished-looking man in front of the capitol building. Jackson sets the photo down, starts rummaging through desk drawers. E)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. POLICE HEADQUARTERS - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Crowder The officer is alleged to be involved in illicit drug trafficking, racketeering and kidnapping -- Above The Law - Rev. 41787 F)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CONVENTION CENTER\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico, in the crush of convention-goers, pauses before a booth promoting a Tv manufacturer. The latest model Tv's are set up in a sales display, with visitors gawking at the pictures of the church bombing aftermath\"}, {\"character\": \"NEWSWOMAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Police sources also speculate that Toscani may be connected to the suspect in the bombing of St. Elizabeth's parish church --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A police composite rendering of the woman who placed the bomb at the church is shown on the television. Newswoman  -- the suspect is likely to be armed and considered to be extremely dangerous -- Nico's police Id photo appears on the news. He blends back into the crowd\"}, {\"character\": \"NEWSWOMAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"In other news, Senator Ernest Harrison's presidential bid has.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico moves swiftly through the convention center floor (which is packed for thousands of square feet with sales booths, each manned by technicians and pitchmen, all displaying the latest in high-tech data processing equipment, telecommunications, etc.) G)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CONDO APARTMENT - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jax stuffs a wad of offical papers -- including appoint- ment books, notes and tapes -- into her briefcase. At the apartment door, she looks both ways, then emerges, starts away down the hallway. H)\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CONVENTION CENTER - COMPUTER BOOTH - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico in the crowd in front of the booth of a Japanese computer manufacturer. Dr. Watanabe (Nico's friend whom we remember from the baptismpicnic scene) is the chief engineer at the booth, showing off some high-tech equipment to several brainy looking executives. Watanabe glances up, spots Nico. Nico makes a subtle sign to indicate he must speak to Watanabe. Watanabe crosses at once to Nico. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 73A. So good to see you again, sir\"}, {\"character\": \"WATANABE\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Come back near closing. five- thirty. we'll place your order then.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico nods, fades like a shadow into the throng. Music Down, Sequence Ends -- Dissolve To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CONVENTION CENTER - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"All customers gone, lights being turned off. Janitors sweep up, the last booth people shut down for the night. Watanabe emerges with Nico from behind a booth divider, leads her old friend at a brisk pace across the deserted floor\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Listen, Wat. you know I wouldn't call in a favor --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Watanabe Of course not. Just because you kept a few 'friendly' tribesmen from cutting my heart out and serving it up as Pad Thai? With a wink, Watanabe escorts Nico into a back area off the floor. packed with super sophisticated computer equipment. Carpeted office dividers set off a small area, Watanabe \\\"boots up\\\" a terminal, sits down with relish\"}, {\"character\": \"WATANABE\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"The last six years I've been risking nothing but money. It's a kick to risk my ass again.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico eyes the equipment and Watanabe, impressed. The old Spook\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"OMITTED\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Cut Away To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. JACKSON'S APARTMENT - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson has the Senator's aide's papers spread before her, cataloging them with interest. The Phone Rings. Jackson picks it up\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Jackson.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Whoever the voice is , it makes Jackson forget the documents. Jackson -- Yes. yes, of course, sister, I know who you are. -- where. where are you?\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. WATANABE'S COMPUTER AREA - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Watanabe working two computers simultaneously, with the gusto of a rock keyboard player. Cut Back To: Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Watanabe -- No way to access Covert Ops directly. But Ornstein's at Princeton, he's got a database bigger than Langley -- (works keyboard lovingly) If I can't crack that turkey's code, it's time to hang up my rock and roll shoes -- Nico watches Watanabe work. Watanabe -- ah, here! Here's a little trap door. into -- Let's see if we can wriggle up (watches the screen with anticipation) Personnel files! Operative dossiers. Will that do? It's a start\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico sits down beside Watanabe\"}, {\"character\": \"FULL ASHTRAY\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Dissolve To:\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Watanabe stubs out a cigarette. Empty coffee cups all around. Nico paces, reading a hard-copy printout\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Fox has had a helluva career.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"'69 to '76, Cambodia, Laos. Operation Phoenix. Operation Green Mountain. Operaton Northstar. This is all Vang Pao, it's all heroin -- You friend has found his metier\"}, {\"character\": \"WATANABE\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico circles the \\\"operations\\\" on the page, hands it to Watanabe\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Run personnel retrievals on all these operations. I want the names of every company man who was on them.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Close - Computer Screen A list of about thirty names -- mostly civilian, but some with military rank attached. Quick Dissolve To: Above The Law - Rev. 41787 75A\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Altshuler. Cosgrove. I know half these guys --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Okay. now run me an update. Where are these fuckers now? Quick Dissolve To: Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Nico - Later Pouring a fresh coffee, studying the screen with Watanabe. Watanabe (finger tracks down screen) Central American desk. Central American desk. Central -\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Thirty names from secret drug operations. and two-thirds of 'em are in Central America.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"All right. Run these two names: Bautista Salvano and Ramon 'Chi Chi' Testamente\"}, {\"character\": \"WATANABE\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Those street dealers you were talking about? They're not gonna be in here.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico gives her a look. Watanabe starts punching keys. Close - Computer Screen Official biographies of Salvano and Chi Chi come up\"}, {\"character\": \"WATANABE\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Well, kiss my ass.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Both former Somoza secret police. Recruited by agency, 1975. Trained Fort Benning, counter insurgency. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 76A. Where's Fox's printout? Nico  1976. Fort Benning. He recruited these pricks! Dissolve To: 270A\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. CONVENTION HALL - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"It's even later. finishing up the huge floor. A few display lights remain on, otherwise it's dark. Nico stands above, observing, contemplating the information he has received. The last of the janitorial crew is\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. WATANABE'S COMPUTER AREA\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Watanabe crapped out in a chair; Nico looking weary, pacing, wracking his brain\"}, {\"character\": \"WATANABE\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"There's nothing left, Nico. We've wrung these files dry.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Nico (muttering to himself; thinking) Fox is here, in Chicago. or was here. . Listen. Can this thing tap into airlines? Reservations records -- I can get you the ball scores, too\"}, {\"character\": \"WATANABE\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Dissolve To\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"As he finishes viewing the screen, stands Five agents from Central American desk. All trained assassins. All arrived in Chicago in the last week -- and none of them has left.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico grabs his coat, gulps a last swallow of coffee -\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Thanks, Wat. You finally may have done some good for your country.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Where are you going\"}, {\"character\": \"WATANABE\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"To find a priest\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Cut To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. CONVENTION CENTER - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson's unmarked car whips into the curb. Aboard: Jackson and Lukich. Nico steps from the shadows, ducks into the back seat. The car takes off.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. UNMARKED CAR - MOVING - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"How did ya find him\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"The nun phoned me. She said two men had been sneaking around the church. She sounded scared --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico checks his .45. Two spare clips\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"There's more. I got the papers from that senator's aide's apartment. Everything Harrison's been working on. It's all at my place.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Cut To: Elevated Subway Train - Night Booms Past Camera, only a few feet away from a row of tenement apartment buildings. As Train sound Recedes, Camera Moves In On one building. We hear Loud Upbeat Rock And Roll coming from a third-floor apartment --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. TENEMENT - POV FROM CAR ON STREET - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Voice  Once you're inside, you'll signal us.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CAR - CLOSEUP ON TREMBLING WOMAN \", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"It is the Middle-aged Woman who left the bomb, seen in Father Genarro's church. A police sketch of her was seen on tele- vision. instructions. talking to her. She is looking up at the third-floor window, getting She turns around occasionally to see who's Salvano  Don't be scared. Your life depends on this. Close On Driver It is one of Salvano's goons we've seen before. He is checking his gun.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. TENEMENT HALLWAY - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"She knocks on a door. We hear Footsteps from The Woman walks slowly down the hall. She carries a small donation can. within the apartment. The door opens. It's Bonifacia, the nun from the church . The Middle-Aged Woman with the donation can raises it as if asking for a contribution. really doesn't want to leave the door open. Bonificia looks flustered, impatient. She Middle-Aged Woman Exusame, por favor. Tiene dinero para.\"}, {\"character\": \"FROM NOWHERE\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Three of Salvano's armed goons appear on both sides of the doorway.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"They push both women violently into the apartment. Closeup - Goon He steps quickly, surely into the apartment. Closeup - Bedroom Door It flies open. The goon points his gun At the Camera\"}, {\"character\": \"GUNMEN'S POV\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Father Tomassino, the Costa Rican priest, stands at the window, he has been trying to open it. He turns. He knows he can't escape.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. APARTMENT - POV FROM SALVANO'S CAR\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The light in the apartment window blinks twice.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. TENEMENT - STREET - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"From two cars emerge the shapes of several men.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. CHICAGO STREET - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Jackson's car -- with Jackson, Nico and Lukich aboard -- swings around a corner into a traffic jam. The Horn Blares.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. TENEMENT APARTMENT - THIRD FLOOR - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A Stereo Speaker Blasts Music from the front room. Camera Pans Across Bonifacia's bedroom dresser. We see mementos of her life and a photo of herself with Father Genarro with a group of children. Camera Continues To Pan Past Bonifacia's bed, Past Bonifacia's body! Camera Continues Down To the floor, where lies the lady who planted the bomb. They both appear dead. Close - Father Tomassino He is in a chair, his wrists strapped to the chair arms. is sweating, fearful but clinging to his courage. He Another Angle Behind Father Tomassino, we see Salvano, Chi Chi and two other goons, armed with pistols. Salvano moves toward the priest, sets a small Tv table down beside him. The priest glances toward it -- Priest'S Pov - Tv Table Atop its rickety surface: a fearsome array of syringes and drug vials. Back To Father ToMASSINO He glances up from the hypodermics -- Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Priest'S Pov Into Frame moves Kurt Zagon! We see clearly the 15 years of aging since Se Asia. His face is even scarier than when he performed similar atrocities in those days. Zagon prepares a syringe, tests it, shooting a clear liquid skyward\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You'll be in heaven in a few minutes, padre. you through hell.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"But first I'm going to put\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. CHICAGO STREET - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico, Lukich and Jackson are speeding through the infamous Southside. We want to scream at them to get there already. Back To Apartment Salvano holds the priest's arm steady, Zagon moves in with the needle\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You came here to talk to the Senator's aide, didn't you?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I tried. But you killed him first\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER TOMASSINO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Who told you about our plans\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER TOMASSINO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"This is from confession. I tell no one\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You wouldn't lie to me, Father? It's a sin.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Father Tomassino says nothing, he begins to cry\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"If you spoke to anyone, tell me now --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"-- and I won't have to use this.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. TENEMENT - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The unmarked police car pulls up, across the street.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. CAR - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico, Jackson, and Lukich gaze at the building. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 80A. 296A Pov From Car In the shadows by the corner, a hulking Latino man loiters. That's an eyeball if I ever saw one. Jackson  296B Back To Car Nico starts to open the car door. Jackson moves to join him. \"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You're our backup. If we come out running, then you can shoot.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico's eyes meet his partner's. It's plain he'll break her leg if he has to, to keep her safe by the car. Jackson accepts this reluctantly.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. TENEMENT - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Lukich exit the vehicle. Nico indicates an adjacent building; he and Lukich start for it.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. APARTMENT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Father Tomassino is beginning to come under the influence of Zagon's chemicals. In spite of this the priest's spirit to resist is astounding. Speak to me, Father -- who did you tell\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER TOMASSINO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I know what you are. I know what beasts you are.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. ADJACENT BUILDING - ROOF OF TENEMENT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Lukich emerge from the roof door, guns drawn. roof is empty. Antennas, skylights, clotheslines. The pair creep soundlessly onto the next roof. They cross toward the roof door like infantrymen, moving one at a time from cover to cover, covering each other. They reach the door that leads down into the building. Nico checks the far side of the enclosure, nods to Lukich. Lukich cracks the roof door open -- The Stairwell From Roof - Nico And Lukich Nico and Lukich creep down the stairs from the roof. Nico opens the door leading to the top floor.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. APARTMENT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The drugs have taken hold. The priest's brain is an open memory bank for Zagon to probe. I want to know who you told\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER TOMASSINO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I told them. you make the ninos. see. castrating their fathers -- raping. mutilating their mothers . And.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \". and sometimes. to the ninos. Nico'S Pov - Hallway As he slowly pushes the door open. The hallway is empty.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. HALLWAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Lukich pad in. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Quickly Lukich checks the stairs leading down. Nico crosses silently past the first apartment door, checks the far end of the hallway. Lukich approaches from the opposite side. They take up positions flanking the door, guns drawn. The Loud Music Continues from inside. Nico comes back toward the apartment door\"}, {\"character\": \"INSIDE APARTMENT\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Salvano and Chi Chi look on, revulsed. Whatever is happening to Father Tomassino is enough to make even cruel men ill.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"-- Tell me the truth, Father -\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"The priest's eyes roll grotesquely; he convulses, sweat beading on his forehead. He looks like a man in the agonies of some narcotic hell.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Zagon -- Can we kill him? If you told anyone, about our plans to kill the senator, we cannot do it. Nadie\"}, {\"character\": \"FATHER TOMASSINO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nadie. Nadie.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico And Lukich In Hallway O.S. we hear another Elevated Train Approaching outside. Nico kicks the apartment door in! He and Lukich burst in, guns clutched two-handed\"}, {\"character\": \"QUICK CUTS\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The first goon reacts, raises his pistol. Lukich Shoots him. Nico Nails the second goon, just as Chi Chi aims his sawed- off pistol-grip shotgun at Nico. Nico has a split second to dive behind a heavy upholstered chair. Chi Chi's Double- Barrel Blast blows the chair into powder. Almost instan- taneously Nico sees the priest -- just as Zagon slashes the priest's throat! Salvano Shoots Lukich point blank, in the shoulder, sending Lukich's gun sailing. Nico, Firing, grabs Lukich, dives out the door with him -\"}, {\"character\": \"HALLWAY\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Zagon and Salvano Open Fire from the apartment full-tilt. Bullets Rip through the Wall, Blasting Wood and Plaster everywhere. Nico shoves Lukich toward the stairwell --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Go! Go! Nico -- Simultaneously Firing back through the kicked-in door, Emptying his Gun. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Zagon (in Spanish, from apartment) Get him! Finish him! At that instant -- A broadside of Bullets slam Nico is slamming a fresh clip in, Lukich is stumbling away toward the stairwell. Salvano and Chi Chi appear in the apartment doorway. Chi Chi levels his fierce \\\"hogleg\\\" at Nico's head. into the wall around Chi Chi. It's Jackson -- on the stairs! Chi Chi is hit, but spins, Fires. His shotgun blast catches Jackson square in the chest, blowing her back like a doll, down the stairwell, out of sight. Nico reacts with agony, twists on the floor, Shoots Chi Chi in the face. Nico pulls the trigger as fast as he can, sending a Hail of Fire through the doorway, through the walls. Salvano clutches his hench- man, using his dead body as a shield; Nico's Bullets blow Chi Chi apart. ribs! Zagon Fires back, hits Nico in the side by the Nico tries to fire back; he's empty! Now\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico bolts for the stairwell to the roof, clawing for a new clip as he goes. Salvano and Zagon burst into the hallway, Shooting at Nico.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Intercut - Elevated Train Thundering along the tracks adjacent to the building.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. ROOF - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico highballs from the stairwell as the tarpaper roof erupts all around him with Gunfire from the floor below! He dives sideways, rolling to avoid the fire -- He recovers his footing in time to see Salvano and Zagon burst onto the roof from the stairwell. Nico's Bullets miss them; they separate, taking cover behind two walls at the roof's margins. Nico is trapped -- in the open. Zagon And Salvano pop back out, aiming at Nico -- Nico leaps off the roof! Angle - Elevated Train - Moving Nico lands on the roof of the speeding \\\"el\\\" train, his momentum nearly carrying him off the far side -- Nico - Atop Train catches a railing, claws at it. Bullets rip into the train roof all around him -- Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Atop Tenement Roof - Salvano And Zagon Fire for all they're worth at Nico's receding form. Atop Train - Nico crawls to the space between cars, lowers himself down. clings to the swaying chains. He 315A\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. TRAIN CAR\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico staggers through the almost empty car and collapses on a bench. Around Corner - Two Police Cars hurtle Into View under the El, Sirens Blaring. Back On Tenement Roof Zagon and Salvano scramble away. Omitted\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. EL STATION - STAIRWAY TO STREET - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Cut To: A cleaner, more upscale neighborhood. Nico labors down the steps, clutching his jacket to his ribs. Several affluent people look at him oddly, he ignores them, keeps going -- He makes his way up the street, weakening, to a tasteful brown- stone. Nico climbs the steps in pain -- Quick Dissolve To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. JACKSON'S APARTMENT - BATHROOM - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico over the sink, shirt off, Water Running -- applying a makeshift bandage to his bloody ribs. We see Jackson's make- up stuff along the counter, feminine robes hanging on the door, law books around a reading stand. Nico is in real pain, exhausted, weakening -- Living Room - Night Nico at Jackson's desk, its surface spread with the notes and papers she got from Senator Harrison's aide's place. glimpse them: bodies, etc. attention shifts -- He tries to study them, quickly, but his photos of Central American atrocities, dead We Nico glances around the apartment: more law books, Jackson's degree on the wall, her rowing machine on the floor, several framed photos beside him on her desk. Nico turns several toward him. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Insert - Framed Photos Jackson with her sisters and their kids, Jackson in law class, Jackson and Nico posing, smiling, at the police shoot- ing range -- Back To Nico He starts to cry. Nico -- Had to be a hero. another fucking hero. I'm sorry Jax. He reaches for a small calendar, looks at it. Closeup - Calendar Nico circles \\\"meet with Father Tomassino.\\\" Nico circles another date, \\\"Senator delivers foreign policy position paperCommittee for Democratic Policy fund raiser.\"}, {\"character\": \"OMITTED\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Back To Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico scoops up the aide's papers, stands, wobbly -- -- Senator. -- Nico -- dumb fuck. think they're gonna let you put 'em outta business -- 327A\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. EMERGENCY ROOM CORRIDOR - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Several cops frantically clear the way to the emergency room. A gurney is wheeled down the corridor. Lukich, a shoulder bandaged, walks beside the gurney, holding the hand of Jackson. 327B Closeup On a bloody flak jacket rests upon the gurney. 327C Closeup - Jackson She's been sedated. She has buckshot wounds on her neck and shoulder, but she is alive\"}, {\"character\": \"JACKSON\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"You call Nico's goddamn Uncle and find out if he's heard anything.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 41787 85A\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You just shutup and take it easy, pal.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. TAXI - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Closeup of Nico riding through the wet streets. 328A\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. EMERGENCY ROOM\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Lukich is on the phone. His shirt is off and he's being bandaged. In the background Jackson is also being cared for\"}, {\"character\": \"LUKICH\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"We don't know what happened to him, Branca. Ya, she's gonna be alright.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"328B\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. BRANCA'S SAFE HOUSE - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Branca, a bodyguard next to him, grimly puts down the phone. He looks devastated. Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. DRIVEWAY - BRANCA'S SAFE HOUSE - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"From the darkness, Nico appears, barely making it up the driveway. We hear the sound of the Cab Drive Off.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. BRANCA'S SAFE HOUSE - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Branca and a bodyguard come forward, grabbing Nico as Nico almost collapses. Jesus Christ\"}, {\"character\": \"BRANCA\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"The motherfuckas got Jackson\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"BRANCA\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Lukich called. She's not dead. She's gonna make it. She was wearing a vest.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico can't believe it. In spite of it all, life comes to him. A little smile. That broad didn't trust me\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Cut To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. BRANCA'S SAFE HOUSE - POV FROM WINDOW - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"We glimpse several armed bodyguards in concealed positions. A late-model Cadillac pulls up. A man carrying a doctor's bag gets out and is escorted to the side door.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. BRANCA'S SAFE HOUSE - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Rosa has pulled back the curtain from the second-floor bed- room window. She witnesses the arrival of the doctor. the bed behind her sleep Sara and Julian. A bodyguard stands outside the bedroom door. On\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. BASEMENT FAMILY ROOM - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The doctor tends Nico. Bloody bandages and antiseptic bottles litter a coffee table. Two guards stand by. Branca is showing Nico an 8-by-11 photograph\"}, {\"character\": \"BRANCA\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"It was picked up with your mail this afternoon.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Insert - Photograph A shot of Nico's family taken from a parked car, in front of the church, the morning of the bombing. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Back To Nico And Branca Nico's grim expression shows he knows just what this means\"}, {\"character\": \"BRANCA\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Don't worry, they're booked on an early plane. tomorrow.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"They'll be out of the country Nico winces as the doctor finishes applying a bandage. the background we hear a Commotion. In\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. BASEMENT STAIRWAY - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A bodyguard tries to fend off the physical and verbal assault from Sara and Rosa. Sara carries Julian.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. BASEMENT FAMILY ROOM - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sara rushes to Nico's side. Nico reaches for her, but the pain stabs him. Oh my God, Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Rosa starts forward, her face in agony at the sight of her wounded son.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He's fine. The boy has ribs of steel\"}, {\"character\": \"BRANCA\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"ROSA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Enough of your humor.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sara clings to Nico's arm, tears in her eyes. Rosa crosses herself. Sara begins to weep. The doctor finishes. There's a long awkward moment. Then: Branca (to doctor and bodyguards) Leave them. Leave them alone.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. FAMILY ROOM - LATER\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Quick Dissolve To: Rosa sits in a chair. Nico on the couch, holding Julian. Sara faces him. is in control of her emotions now. Tears have stained her cheeks, but she Sara -- You've got to do it, Nico. You know you have to. Whatever Sara is proposing, Nico is dead set against it. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Rosa Listen to her, Nicola. Whatever you think of him, Federico is family. He is our family. Nico makes no response. Instead, he lifts Julian, nuzzles him tenderly\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Ever notice how clean babies smell? Like nothing in the world has touched them yet.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sara glances to Rosa. Rosa knows what she wants. Dis- creetly Rosa rises, exits. Sara and Nico are alone. If you won't go to him, I will\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Don't push me like this --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Her eyes meet his -- loving, but desperate\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Branca can put us on a plane -- but where can we fly to? Tibet? The moon? There's nowhere they can't find us\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You don't know what the hell you're talking about\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"I'm talking about everything I've learned from you in the past five years.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico is in agony. You know I can't go to him\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Sara takes both his hands in hers\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"Do you know why I love you? Do you know what it is about you that I've always loved?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(as Nico fights his own emotion) It's what you have inside. Pride. You don't live the way other people live. right and won't let anyone or anything make you stray from it. You trust what you see as Above The Law - Rev. 42987 88A. Move In Past Sara To Nico's face\"}, {\"character\": \"SARA\", \"gender\": 0, \"line\": \"But now that pride may kill all of us.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You've got to swallow that pride, Nico. Lay it aside. Choke on it if you have to. Another Angle - Nico And Sara Close together, with their baby between them. Sara buries her face against her husband's chest. Nico's arm goes around her. He holds her tight. Cut To: Close - Nico - Against Wall - Day He wears a suit and tie, a hat. All business. Is this the attorney\"}, {\"character\": \"MAN\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You can come now, Mr. Carlucci\"}, {\"character\": \"ANOTHER MAN\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"O.S. we hear a Metallic sound Begin, Very Close -- Pull Back To\"}, {\"character\": \"ANOTHER ANGLE\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"To reveal bars which slide electrically to the side. A prison door opens, letting him through.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Angle - Prison Corridor - Day Nico, escorted by a prison guard, walks down a long, blank hallway. Cut To\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Waiting in a barren reception room. Several benches, tables; heavy steel mesh over windows --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico'S Pov - Across Room A steel door opens on the far side. Out steps a small Italian man in his seventies, wearing the faded denim of an inmate. Above The Law - Rev. 42987\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. PRISON CORRIDOR - LONG SHOT - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"88B-90. Nico and the small man walk together down a long corridor, speaking occasionally, the tension thick between them. two armed prison officials. Behind them, a discreet fifteen paces, walk Closer - Larusso And Nico The old man never looks directly at Nico, yet we sense keenly that he is taking the younger man's measure\"}, {\"character\": \"FREDERICO LARUSSO\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I am only an old man. An old man with a cancer.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The two are like an old and a young lion, appraising each other -- using all five senses and more\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I don't have much time, Uncle. So I must speak plainly.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Larusso listens. Nico waits for a beat. Then: Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Nico (this is very painful for him) -- For as long as I've been old enough to think, I've hated you and hated everything you stood for. Larusso takes this in without a flicker\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I was so sure that you and I were on opposite sides of the fence. and that you and your people were destroying this country --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico pauses, glances away across the grounds. Nico -- The most painful realization of my life was that the people I worked for and you are not far apart. -- And there's not much difference between what you are and what I was. Larusso studies Nico a long moment. Then takes Nico's elbow. \"}, {\"character\": \"OMITTED\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico And Larusso\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"continue across the grounds\"}, {\"character\": \"FREDERICO LARUSSO\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I will be candid with you. I knew, probably before you did, that you would be coming to me. I knew what you would ask. and I had every intention of refusing you.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He glances to Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"FREDERICO LARUSSO\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"But it is a form of wisdom to know when to cease relying only upon yourself.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He keeps walking\"}, {\"character\": \"FREDERICO LARUSSO\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You know, of course, that this Senator Harrison will never live to make his speech tomorrow.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"You know, too, that as long as this man. this torturer -- Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Kurt Zagon\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FREDERICO LARUSSO\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"-- As long as this Zagon lives, nothing I can do will guarantee your family's safety.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"'Ecce non uomine, ecce bestie.' You know Dante? 'These are not men, these are animals.' Larusso stops, takes a small note pad from his pocket. quickly scribbles a few lines. He Memorize this address\"}, {\"character\": \"FREDERICO LARUSSO\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He holds the paper for Nico to see.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Have you got it in your mind\"}, {\"character\": \"FREDERICO LARUSSO\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico nods.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Larusso tears the paper into tiny shreds.\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. ADMIN BUILDING - RECEPTION ROOM - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The old man takes his leave of Nico with a warm, if formal handshake. The guards stand by, waiting\"}, {\"character\": \"FREDERICO LARUSSO\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Thank you, Mr. Carlucci. I trust you will give my love to my niece, Rosa\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I will do that, Mr. Larusso.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I hope you will be well. Larusso nods: back through the steel door. \\\"Bene.\\\" Then: without a word he turns and exits\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. O'HARE AIRPORT - BOARDING GATE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Cut To: Passengers file aboard a flight to Toronto. Hugs, goodbyes. Rosa, carrying the baby, is among the crowd moving toward the boarding door. Leaving with them are two of Branca's men. fringes, looking inobtrusive but definitely on guard. We Pick Out Branca and two of his bodyguards near the Above The Law - Rev. 42987 92A93. Corner Near Branca Hidden by a bank of phones, Sara clings to Nico, holding him as tight as she can. When she releases him, we can't hear what she says, but it seems like, \\\"Be careful, please be careful.\\\" hurry. Nico glances to Branca, who motions subtly to He squeezes Sara's hand, she joins the crowd swelling toward the boarding door -- Cut To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. O'HARE - RUNWAY - DAY \", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"An Air Canada Plane Blasts skyward. Nico And Branca watch from an open corner of a parking lot. As the plane begins its bank to gain altitude, Branca turns to Nico. The two bodybuards keep a discreet watch nearby\"}, {\"character\": \"BRANCA\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You got the architect's drawings? Wiring, floor plans --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico indicates a briefcase he is carrying. It's all here\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico turns to his uncle. Regards him with affection.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I could help you from here on\"}, {\"character\": \"BRANCA\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"It's not your business\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico embraces his uncle by both shoulders.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Grazie, tio caro\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Branca pats Nico's cheek.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Take care of yourself, Nicola\"}, {\"character\": \"BRANCA\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Cut To:\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Series Of Shots Several Shots of high-rise cityscapes at night. Dissolve To: Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Omitted thru Telescope Pov - Chicago Skyline - Night Camera Pans To the apartment complex across the plaza. Focus On one suite on the topmost floor. Curtains are drawn on all windows, but through one crack we glimpse a man pacing. The man wears a white shirt and a shoulder holster. Raise Telescope Pov To the roof of the apartment complex. We see a heli-pad. Two more men, also in suits -- smoking, talking. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Lower Telescope Pov Back To the apartment suite. Now another man crosses before the gap in the curtains. Wearing a cowboy hat: Zagon! He's laughing, pouring himself a drink at the wet bar --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. ROOFTOP SKYSCRAPER - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico, looking through a high-tech night telescope. His briefcase is by his feet, open. Several architect's drawings, floor plans visible. Nico lifts his eye from the scope, jots a note on a pocket pad\"}, {\"character\": \"VOICE\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Not even you can hit him at this range, Nico.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"O.S. behind Nico: the unmistakable sound of a .45 Safety being Clicked Off. Nico freezes, his back to the voice. raises his hands. He That wasn't the plan, Nelson\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nelson Fox\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"covers Nico from behind with a silencer-fitted .45. He glances to the briefcase and building plans, on the floor\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Close range, huh? Never work. Place is rigged, scanned every 35 seconds\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I was thinking of a mine on the roof. Remote-triggered, when the chopper comes in\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Roof's wired too. Sensors every fifteen feet.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Fox's finger rests ready on the trigger. You can turn now. Slowly. Slooowly.\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"We see Fox clearly now. His boyish features\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico turns. have weathered since his \\\"spook\\\" days in Vietnam. There is grey in his hair now: he wears an expensive suit and is alone. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Fox I figured you'd do your recon from this building. Nico regards his old mate across the gun barrel. You're looking fit, Nelson\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Getting a bit of a tire\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Your own tailor?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Hong Kong\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You've gone a long way\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Fox motions for Nico to dump his gun; Nico complies, dropping it gently into the briefcase. Nico takes half a step toward Fox.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Fox shakes his head in warning. Uh uh. Uhhh-uh.\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I know what you can do when you get too close to a man.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Closeup - Nico I don't believe you, Fox. Nico 367A\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. BUILDING CORRIDOR - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico walks, hands behind his head. Fox is catty-corner be- hind him, carrying the briefcase, .45 leveled at Nico's back.  Fox -- What's so hard to believe. I want to help you, you dumb guinea! Fox the fixer\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"If I wanted to cap you, I'd have saved myself this chit-chat. Make big points for me to bring in your scalp. I'd be White House material\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Is that what Zagon is? One of your basement boys?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 41787 96A\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Zagon's a rancher. 4000 acres in Costa Rica. Beautiful place.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Bought with what -- opium from Cambodia\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"And a ton a week of coke from other places\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Which he funnels here through Salvano. With the Company getting its cut.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Legal tender\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Still dodging appropriations committees, eh, Nelson?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"That's my job, Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"They arrive at an elevator Keep your nose in the corner. When we get out, stay five paces ahead of me.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Cross down to the garage. 367B\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. LOWER CORRIDOR\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico and Fox emerge from the elevator. Nico lowers his hands from behind his head. Fox keeps his gun out of sight as he and Nico step past. Elevator Bank - Night Fox maintains a slight distance behind Nico as they cross to- ward some escalators under a sign: \\\"To Parking Level 8.\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"The Senator couldn't be bought, could he? you cleared Zagon to frost him --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He was gonna blow the lid off, so Keep walking. Fox\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. PARKING STRUCTURE\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"They reach a corner and turn. 97A\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"But the priest found out somehow and ran here. You couldn't do the Senator's number 'till you knew if the priest had talked. So Zagon flew in with his little medical bag. Only by then I was in on it -- and you thought I might recognize his handiwork.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Parking Garage - Valet Station Several guests and diners wait by the cashier's booth for their cars to be fetched. Valets hustle with tickets. and Nico come off the escalator. Fox Fox If your name was Joe Smith I never would have caught it. But how many Nicola Toscani's are there? You got it off the arrest sheet\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Fox hands his ticket to the cashier, motions Nico to the side, away from the guests, still keeping his distance -- should Nico try to make a move\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I tried to warn you, old buddy. I knew you had wiretaps. and I knew you wouldn't let 'em go\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Only I was too dumb to crack it. I was so busy trying to figure a code, I didn't even recognize Zagon's voice.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"It's all crystal clear to Nico now. So we kill our own senators now\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Why not? The Romans did\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"A Cadillac pulls up; the valet hops out, two particularly florid, well-fed guests get in, tipping the valet.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico (to Fox, watching the guests) Are we the Romans? We're an empire too\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Fox doesn't like the look Nico gives him Would you rather spoon borscht and quote Lenin?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"I'm trying to save you, asshole! I got a spot for you. Thailand, deep under, no names, no numbers -- Doing what -- processing heroin\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You 'consult.' You 'assist.' You send checks to your family. Zagon won't touch you, you'll be on the team --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Fuck you\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"In five years you're out, with a fat Swiss account and a Gs-15 pension.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico stares at his old friend with contempt. He sees the gun under Fox's coat, but he's too tired and too disgusted to care -\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"You know, Fox, right now in Israel they're trying some 80-year-old camp guard for war crimes. And all around our country there are guys on Death Row for killing one person, two people. And probably they all deserve it --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He takes a step toward Fox. Fox's hand tightens on his gun. Nico -- but you and I know a couple guys personally who are responsible for the murder of at least what. 60,000 non- military personnel. Lao. Thai. Cambodian. Viet. Librarians, teachers, doctors. women, children. and that's just a sliver of it. Fox tries to maintain a hard face. But his own guilty conscience is working -\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"We've wiped out entire fucking countries. And not one agent --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Fox (moves gun into Nico's view) Stop right there! Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Nico -- not one C.I.A. agent has ever been tried or convicted, much less accused of any crimes. You motherfuckers think you're above the law -- Well, you ain't above mine. Nico holds himself, trembling with intensity. At that moment -- of Approaching Tires. Nico and Fox turn to see -- O.S. from the garage entrance ramp: the Squeal Note 4-17-87. The Following Sequence Will Be Modified To Conform To Location. Do Not Build Or Purchase Without Checking With Stunt COOrDINAToR And Assistant DIRECToRS\"}, {\"character\": \"WEEK.\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Storyboards And New Pages Will Be Available Next\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A Big Car Screeches to a halt in front of them. Five men dismount swiftly. tenement. and Zagon! Salvano, Bad Dude, and two agent types from the Zagon and his men are forty feet from Nico and Fox, playing it cool so as not to alarm any innocent bystanders, but the bulk under their jackets is unmistakably guns\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Well. well. What a team we have here\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"We've been looking for you, Nelson. I see you've found our friend.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Fox looks shaky, unnerved: Nico's words have hit too close to home. One of Zagon's agents holds their car's rear door open. Now Nico backs away a step, ready for anything. Thanks for the help, Fox\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I didn't bring him, Nico. I swear it\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Have you two been sharing fond memories? Reminiscing about the good old days?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Zagon waves Nico and Fox toward his car. Zagon and Salvano start forward. Fox glances, torn, to Nico, who has backed away another half-step. Will Nico attack? Run for it? Fox 100A. Stay still! Don't fucking move!! Fox pulls his .45 from concealment, covering Nico. An Evening-Gowned Woman, waiting with her husband for their car, hears Fox's shout, sees his gun. Evening Gown Woman Jack -- The husband sees. So do the other guests. Salvano sees their alarm; he swings his jacket open, revealing a snub machine gun. Someone Screams -- Bring in our friend, Nelson\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Salvano's muzzle covers Fox and Nico --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Be a good boy -\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"NA\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"His moment of truth.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Dive, Nico!\"}, {\"character\": \"FOX\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Pandemonium. Fox, dying, slings his .45 to Nico, who\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He Fires -- at Salvano! In the same instant, Salvano pulls his own trigger! Salvano's Machine Gun Burst cuts Fox down, a milli-second before Fox's .45 Slug Blows Salvano off his feet! snatches it from the ground just as a Hail of Machine Gun Fire Thunders around him. Nico dives headlong behind a concrete column, which is instantly chewed to shreds by GunFire. second agent hurries forward to outflank Nico. Nico pops from behind the column, Drills the agent broadside behind the ear, blowing the whole side of his head off! Guests and valets are shrieking in terror, hitting the deck in clusters, clawing and scrambling over each other for safety. Zagon Fires his Mac-10 on full automatic. A Zagon (to first agent, advancing) Move! Nico springs from cover, Firing, trying to bolt down the garage ramp, toward the lower levels. His path puts the first agent directly in Zagon's line of fire. Zagon doesn't hesitate; he Opens Up on Nico, cutting down his own man -- Salvano has gotten to his feet, wounded, but still handling his gun. He joins Zagon, rushing forward -- Ramp To Lower Levels A valet rounds a corner, unsuspecting, bringing up a car. Nico is on him like a cat, tearing the poor boy from behind the wheel, leaping in -- Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Zagon And Salvano tear around the corner at the top of the ramp. Both Open Fire as -- Nico - In Car highballs straight toward them! Salvano hold the trigger down, Full Automatic -\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO'S CAR\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico drops below the dash, driving blind. The Windshield is Blown Apart, both Front Tires Explode, the Radiator Blasts Steam -\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Reloading as Salvano Fires.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico'S Car pinwheels out of control, its nose facing away from Salvano and Zagon. The car Brakes Furiously -- Nico hits reverse, looking back over the seat -- Nico'S Pov - Through Rear Car Window He sees Salvano, his clip empty now, hurrying to wrestle a fresh magazine in -- Angle - Nico'S Car And Salvano Nico floors it in reverse, slamming into Salvano, lifting him off his feet, smashing him with the car into a metal grate wall\"}, {\"character\": \"SALVANO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"A horrible death.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"383A\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. PARKING STRUCTURE - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"From the eighth floor the metal grate of the parking struc- ture blows out onto the street below, followed by Salvano's body. Nico - Behind The Wheel Burning Rubber Furiously, away from the wall -\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Reloaded, turning his gun toward Nico, when --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Two Uniformed Hotel Security Guards hurtle around the corner from the escalators, guns drawn. 102A. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 First Security Guard You there -- Zagon spins, rips both guards with a Fierce Burst! The Guards drop. Zagon turns to -- Nico - Out Of Car on his feet, charging straight at Zagon. Nico grabs him, slams Zagon with incredible force into a concrete column. Zagon's gun goes flying, but miraculously he spins away. Nico dives for him, gets his neck in a grip that is certain to snap it in half a second. But -- Zagon'S Knife appears in the torturer's hand. It slashes Nico, right a- cross his already wounded ribs! Nico cries in agony -- Zagon scampers free. between Zagon and Zagon's machine gun on the ground. Zagon bolts for his car. Nico dives for the gun -- Nico gets to his feet, bleeding. Nico is Car Zagon floors it into a Scorching 360, Blasts up the exit ramp, out of Nico's line of fire -- Nico leaps into the other, half-destroyed car. Its two front tires are flat, windshield blown out, Radiator Pouring Steam. Nico does the only thing he can do: puts the pedal to the metal in reverse, Blasts across the ramp divider, takes off after Zagon in reverse -- On Ramp - ZAGOn'S Car Another car is coming down. Zagon sideswipes it into a wall, keeps going -- On Ramp - Nico'S Wrecked Car Rear Tires Churning smoke, Front Flats Scraping on their rims. he pours on the speed -- Top Of Ramp - Hotel Access Drive Zagon's car whips out into the night-time commotion. Pedestrians, Police Sirens O.S. Zagon looks behind him -- Nico'S Car - Top Of Ramp hurtles into view in reverse! Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Zagon'S Car is trapped by the traffic. Zagon looks around wildly, then floors the accelerator. Zagon's car bucks straight up the pedestrian steps, onto the plaza! Strollers scream and scatter as it fishtails wildly, careening toward the huge stone fountain -- Nico'S Wrecked Car Follows, pouring smoke, in reverse! Nico cuts Zagon off, Crashes into Zagon's car broadside, sending it skittering sideways into the fountain retaining wall -- Zagon leaps free, sprints toward the hotel alley. Nico takes off after him on foot --\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. ALLEY - REAR OF HOTEL - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Zagon races down the darkest of alleys, rounds a corner -- Nico hurtles after him, gaining. Nico whips around the alley corner, straight into: Four Armed Agents waiting beside a plain grey Tv remote van. Nico skitters to a stop as a shotgun, an M-16 and two pistols cover him. Shotgun Agent raises his weapon to fire -\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I want him! I want him alive!\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"No!\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. MIDLAND HOTEL - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A banner reads: Welcome Committee For Democratic Policy\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. ANOTHER ALLEY - BEHIND MIDLAND HOTEL - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A car pulls up. basement of the hotel. Zagon follows. Nico, his wrists tied, is dragged into the\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. BASEMENT ROOM - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sweating, windowless concrete. Overhead pipes. Churning machinery. As the Camera Reveals this airtight dungeon -- Cut To: Pistol Agent  -- this is bullshit, Zagon. We got work to do. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 Zagon  All work and no play makes Jack a dull boy. Nico in a metal chair, wrists taped in front of him. One agent stands behind him, clasping a thin cable noose wrapped tight around Nico's throat. Shotgun agent holds his weapon on him, its twin muzzles inches from Nico's skull. Zagon finishes washing his hands in an industrial-type sink. is cleaned up, wearing a fresh shirt, his hair combed. When he dries his hands, he looks like a surgeon preparing to operate. He Zagon We've got an hour before the honorable senator. (hands towel to pistol agent) You've got to learn to take time, smell the roses. Zagon turns to Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"How are you gonna do him, Zagon? In a motorcade? Or passing through a hotel kitchen?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Zagon motions to slacken off. He stops at a The Noose agent jerks his cable tight, making Nico gag and choke. small table before Nico -- unrolls a well-worn felt pouch. Zagon watches Nico's reaction as the tools of the inter- rogator's trade come into view -- drug vials, syringes, scalpels, surgical tools\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"I've used these little beauties many times to extract information --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(lifts a needle to the light) -- This'll be the first time I've ever used them. just for fun. Zagon sets the syringe down, slips on a heavy, weighted glove\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Take his arms.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Pistol agent and Bad Dude move in, one on each side, seizing Nico's forearms. Shotgun agent holds his weapon tight to Nico's head. Zagon punches Nico square in the face, so hard the chair reels backward, spinning out from under Nico -- Hold him up\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Again. Nico's cheekbone is broken; blood drains\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Pistol agent and Bad Dude lift Nico. Zagon slams him again. from his nose. Zagon aims a two-handed blow; backhands Nico, crushing the other side of his face! Zagon backs off, chest heaving. Pistol agent and Bad Dude plop Nico back in the chair, gagging, choked by the noose. Nico looks like the Viet prisoner -- the one we saw in the opening sequence. Like the prisoner, Nico takes his beating -- still conscious, still meeting Zagon's eyes with defiance\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"This is where you came in, Toscani. Only, now it's where you're gonna check out.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"He takes off his glove, grabs the syringe. Pistol agent and Bad Dude clamp Nico's right arm down tight. Zagon injects Nico. Nico reacts instantly to the hypo -- cursing, sputtering under the choking noose. He twists wildly trying to free him- self, but the agents' powerful arms hold him\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"That's it. Fight it, cherry. Fight it, so it speeds faster on its way --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico struggles more violently\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Fight it. Till the vessels burst in your brain. Till the arteries rupture in your heart --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Slowly, the struggle goes out of Nico. His muscles go limp; he slumps -- drooling, babbling incoherently\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"That's my boy. That's what I was waiting for --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Zagon produces his famous knife. He motions Pistol agent and Bad Dude to release Nico's arms. Noose agent slackens his grip on the choke cable. Zagon moves in closer, gloating, cooing -\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"A fool learns from his own mistakes. But a wise man learns from the mistakes of others --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"(moves closer, blade in hand) You should have killed me when you had the chance, Toscani -- Nico spins instantly to find: the Shot- The blade moves to Nico's throat. Suddenly: Nico springs to life (catching Noose man by surprise and jerking the cable from his grip) -- grabbing Zagon with his taped hands by the throat, lifting him bodily, slamming him ferociously into the wall! Zagon drops to the floor, half-conscious. gun agent right behind him, raising his weapon to Nico's face, about to pull the trigger. Nico sidesteps, grabbing the man's wrist. The Shotgun Goes Off, missing Nico by inches, blasting a huge chunk out of the concrete wall. The Noose agent draws his weapon from his shoulder holster. Nico snaps the Shotgun agent's wrist, flipping him through the air, simultaneously grabbing the weapon, spinning behind the Noose agent, then using the shotgun barrel like a club to smash the back of his head in! Another swing wipes out Pistol agent. Bad Dude, now with a clear shot, aims his M-16. Nico blows him away with a double-barreled Shotgun Blast. In a flash, Nico has spun to Zagon's surgical tool table, lifted a rzor-sharp scalpel and slashed the tape, freeing his hands. He yanks the choke cable off his neck -- Zagon - Against Wall On his feet again. He reaches swiftly to the floor, snatches up his famous knife. Nico confronts him -- face battered, bloody -- shaking, battling internal spasms\"}, {\"character\": \"ZAGON\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Can you feel the chemicals, cherry? You can't fight 'em much longer --\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Long enough to finish you\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"Nico traps the knife, and enters, smashes Zagon\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Sweating, half-spitting, Zagon slashes at Nico like an animal -- in the face with one lightning blow. We see Zagon's nose and face completely cave in. Nico comes under Zagon's elbow, the arm that still holds the knife clamping it in a vise-like grip and bending it backwards, slowly, against the joint -- which now starts to rip in half. Zagon is screaming and cursing, writhing in agony -- The drugs have hit Nico full force now. He's weakening, his eyes are starting to roll. Zagon tries one last surge of strength to save himself; it almost seems he'll wriggle free when: ing sound. the elbow Joint Snaps in half with a sicken- Above The Law - Rev. 42987 As the joint hangs, dangling grotesquely, Nico reaches up around Zagon's neck, still holding the dangling limb with one arm. He begins to now do to Zagon's neck what he did to his arm. crumples to the floor. Nico, in delirium, staggers toward the door -- We hear a terminal Crack. Zagon's body\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. HOTEL LOBBY - REAR STAIRWELL - NIGHT\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A woman at a pay phone. She turns, drops the receiver in shock as -- Nico bursts, delirious, from the stairwell door! Main Lobby - Front Entrance A commotion as Lukich, Agent Neeley and Jackson, arm in a sling, race in from their car. Main Lobby - Rear - Nico weaves wildly forward. He drops to his knees. Guests react in astonishment and horror. 412A Jackson is the first to spot Nico. She runs up to him as he collapses. 412B Nico looks at Jackson. Lukich And Neeley reach Nico and Jackson. Lukich (shouting for anyone) Is there a hotel doctor? Call 911! Above The Law - Rev. 41787 108A. Nico passes out in Jackson's arms. Behind them we see a banner, announcing Senator Harrison's address. From the ballroom we hear Cheers and Applause. A fiery address is being finished inside. The senator is now leaving. Full Shot - Lobby Total confusion. office, a man with a medical bag comes running. The senator sees the group around Nico. Guests staring everywhere. From a side Fade Out. Fade In On:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. NICO'S HOUSE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Press vans outside; a crush of cars, reporters, neighbors. Newsmen are trying to gain access to the house, held back by several cops and some of Nico's more strapping relatives. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Buick Station Wagon escorted by two police motorcycles, pulls in. The press surrounds it as Lukich, Neeley, Lieutenant Strozah and Jackson, her arm in a sling, disembark from the car. 417A Second Car Neeley walks over and opens the door as a court pulls up. stenographer, carrying her transcription machine case, steps out -- followed by a federal judge, Clayton Alspaugh and Senator Ernest Harrison. Reporters shove mikes and cameras at the senator and the judge, shouting questions. Lukich, Neeley and Strozah clear a path for them.  Angle From Inside House - Through Front Window Harrison and Alspaugh fend off the questions, cross the path and mount the steps to the house. T.V. Reporter  -- Senator Harrison has today issued a statement calling for the appointment of a special prosecutor -- Cut To:\"}]}, {\"header\": \"INT. NICO'S HOUSE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico, propped up on the couch, looking like hell, but de- finitely conscious and in full command of his faculties. Sara, Jackson, and Rosa beside him\"}, {\"character\": \"TV\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"A network Anchor delivers the headline news\"}, {\"character\": \"ANCHOR\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Earlier this week, the Harrison Commission delivered its report on the growing C.I.A. scandal to Congress.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The image changes to Senator Harrison behind a battery of microphones, sitting at a senate hearing-type table, with a plaque reading \\\"Sen. Ernest Harrison\\\" before him. Senator Harrison  -- officially-sanctioned deceit, murder and corruption, will continue until these men are brought to justice. Above The Law - Rev. 41787 109A. Nico looks up as the real Senator Harrison, Judge Alspaugh and the others enter the room. Tv Sound Down. Harrison stops before Nico, taking a moment to look with respect and ad- miration at the man propped up on the pillows. Above The Law - Rev. 42987 Senator Harrison Detective Toscani. I wanted to personally thank you. You are making it possible for a sliver of truth to finally come out. He holds out his hand. Nico takes it. The senator gestures to Judge Alspauch\"}, {\"character\": \"SENATOR HARRISON\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"And this is Clayton Alspaugh of the fifth circuit court.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Your Honor\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"The Judge nods to his stenographer, who swiftly sets up her equipment, takes a seat. Rosa makes a face at Branca, who rises, clearing a seat for the Judge. Sara moves in tight beside Nico\"}, {\"character\": \"JUDGE ALSPAUGH\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Are you sure you're feeling well enough?\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Nico glances to Sara, to the supporting faces around him. Lukich. Neeley. Strozah. Jackson. The others\"}, {\"character\": \"NICO\", \"gender\": 1, \"line\": \"If you're ready to listen, I'm ready to talk.\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"Close - Stenographer'S Hands As the Judge's Voice begins Over, \\\"slating\\\" the depo- sitions, the stenographer's fingers start moving. Pull Back To: Angle From Outside Room The full scene. officials recording it -- Nico telling his story. Responsible\"}]}, {\"header\": \"EXT. YARD OUTSIDE NICO'S HOUSE - DAY\", \"dialogues\": [{\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The press corps, vans, neighbors -- Closing Credits Begin. Long Pullback to the street, the houses, and finally: the neighborhood. Nico's neighborhood, to which the truth has finally come home. Closing Credits Continue Over\"}, {\"character\": \"FADE OUT.\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"The End\"}, {\"character\": \"NA\", \"gender\": \"NA\", \"line\": \"This Script Was Prepared By Warner Bros. Inc. Script Processing Department\"}]}], \"char_genders\": {\"HIS\": 1, \"NICO\": 1, \"IRRITABLY\": 1, \"ZAGON\": 1, \"DEFENSIVE POSITION - NICO\": 1, \"THE PRISONER\": 1, \"THE FIRST PRISONER AS A FIGHT REFEREE TO TWO BOXERS\": 1, \"FOX GRABS NICO\": 1, \"THE CIT MAN\": 1, \"HIS SON\": 1, \"THE LAW - REV. 42987 BACK YARD JACKSON\": 0, \"JACKSON\": 0, \"NICO'S MOM\": 0, \"WATANABE\": 1, \"HIS MOTHER\": 0, \"A 60-ISH GRANDMOTHER ZINGARO, WHO IS CRYING\": 1, \"THE POOR WOMAN\": 0, \"MRS. ZINGARO\": 0, \"NICO KISSES MRS. Z.\": 1, \"HE\": 1, \"ONE MAN -- NICO LUNGES FOR THE BAD DUDE\": 1, \"DOORWAY NICO\": 1, \"THREE YOUNG STUDS\": 0, \"THE PIMP\": 1, \"HIM\": 1, \"CARLA DECARLO\": 0, \"NICO TIGHTENS\": 1, \"SHE\": 0, \"A TEARFUL LUCY\": 0, \"CARLA\": 0, \"NARDO\": 1, \"CHI CHI\": 1, \"CHI CHI SHOOTS\": 1, \"SALVANO\": 1, \"OFFICE WINDOW CHI CHI\": 1, \"REAR DINING ROOM FROM THE BACK HALLWAY SALVANO\": 1, \"HER\": 0, \"ANOTHER ANGLE - LINCOLN NICO\": 1, \"NICO'S HUGE HAND GRABS SALVANO'S THROAT\": 1, \"AGENT NEELEY\": 1, \"ONE MAN\": 1, \"LUKICH\": 1, \"HALLORAN\": 1, \"THE LAW - REV. 41787 FATHER GENARRO\": 1, \"FATHER GENARRO\": 1, \"THE LITTLE ONE\": 0, \"CLOSEUP - NICO\": 1, \"A NUN\": 0, \"SARA AND JULIAN\": 0, \"NICO GRABS NEELEY BY BOTH LAPELS\": 1, \"HIMSELF\": 1, \"SEVERAL TOUGH GUYS WE SAW\": 1, \"THE GUY\": 1, \"GUN MAN\": 1, \"NICO FLIPS MACHETE MAN\": 1, \"PIPE MAN'S\": 1, \"BAT MAN\": 1, \"MACHETE MAN\": 1, \"MACHETE\": 1, \"JAX\": 0, \"SARA\": 0, \"FOX\": 1, \"FOX  \": 1, \"O.S.\": 1, \"JULIAN BAWLS\": 1, \"THE BABY\": 1, \"STROZAH\": 1, \"THE NUN\": 0, \"BONIFACIA\": 0, \"NICO'S CAR\": 1, \"THE SIG SAUR .45\": 1, \"THE MAN\": 1, \"A PAKISTANI COUNTER CLERK\": 1, \"A MAN\": 1, \"UNCLE BRANCA\": 1, \"A LARGE PIECE OF DUCTING FROM THE BASEMENT HEATER\": 1, \"THE CLERK\": 1, \"JACKSON OUTSIDE AN APARTMENT DOOR IN A YUPPIE-ESQUE CONDO COMPLEX\": 0, \"JACKSON ENTERS\": 0, \"ID PHOTO\": 1, \"THE LAW - REV. 42987 NICO\": 1, \"THE WOMAN\": 0, \"CLOSEUP - GOON\": 1, \"ACROSS BONIFACIA'S BEDROOM DRESSER\": 0, \"CLOSE - FATHER TOMASSINO\": 1, \"THE PRIEST\": 1, \"FATHER TOMASSINO\": 1, \"CAR NICO\": 1, \"NICO'S\": 1, \"HIS HENCH- MAN\": 1, \"TRAIN - NICO\": 1, \"LIVING ROOM - NIGHT NICO AT JACKSON'S DESK\": 1, \"CLOSEUP - JACKSON\": 0, \"BRANCA\": 1, \"ROSA\": 0, \"BRANCA NICO'S\": 1, \"JULIAN\": 1, \"THE LAW - REV. 42987 ROSA LISTEN TO HER, NICOLA\": 1, \"NICO'S ARM\": 1, \"THE SMALL MAN\": 1, \"THE LAW - REV. 41787 NICO\": 1, \"LARUSSO\": 1, \"THE OLD MAN\": 1, \"A WORD\": 1, \"ANOTHER MAN\": 1, \"HER HUSBAND\": 1, \"NICO'S POV - THROUGH\": 1, \"ZAGON'S GUN\": 1, \"RAMP - NICO\": 1, \"A PLAIN GREY TV REMOTE VAN\": 1, \"SHOTGUN AGENT\": 1, \"JACK A DULL BOY\": 1, \"THE VIET PRISONER -- THE ONE WE SAW IN THE OPENING SEQUENCE\": 1, \"NOOSE AGENT\": 1, \"NOOSE MAN\": 1, \"THE NOOSE AGENT\": 1, \"BAD DUDE\": 1, \"A WOMAN AT A PAY PHONE\": 0, \"MAIN LOBBY - REAR - NICO WEAVES\": 1, \"412A JACKSON\": 0, \"\\\"SEN. ERNEST HARRISON\": 1}}"